WEBVTT

00:33.791 --> 00:35.291
<i>Woohoo!</i>

00:35.333 --> 00:37.083
<i>Ya-haa!</i>

00:37.125 --> 00:40.500
<i>Hurry, friends!</i>
<i>Time for another adventure!</i>

00:40.541 --> 00:43.041
<i>Adventure? I'm in! Yee-hoo!</i>

00:43.083 --> 00:44.291
<i>Let's go, ponies.</i>

00:44.333 --> 00:46.458
<i>Earth ponies, take the lead!</i>

00:46.500 --> 00:48.750
<i>Pegasi, fly beside me!</i>

00:48.791 --> 00:51.041
<i>Unicorns, horns at the ready!</i>

00:51.083 --> 00:53.833
<i>ALL: For Equestria!</i>

00:53.875 --> 00:56.541
<i>What fantastical foe awaits us,</i>
<i>Princess?</i>

00:56.583 --> 00:58.833
<i>Is it something scary?</i>

00:58.875 --> 01:00.708
<i>Or is it something awesome?!</i>

01:00.750 --> 01:03.750
<i>No matter what it is,</i>
<i>we'll face it together.</i>

01:04.833 --> 01:07.708
<i>For we are</i>
<i>the Guardians of Friendship.</i>

01:07.750 --> 01:11.083
<i>With the power of our friendship</i>
<i>and magic, we will...</i>

01:11.125 --> 01:13.416
<i>- Spread love!</i>
<i>- Give hugs!</i>

01:13.458 --> 01:15.000
<i>- Fry brains!</i>
<i>- Huh?</i>

01:15.041 --> 01:16.083
<i>Wait, what?</i>

01:16.125 --> 01:19.666
<i>Yeah, I'm a unicorn, and we're evil!</i>

01:19.708 --> 01:22.833
<i>I'm gonna zap everypony</i>
<i>with my horn lasers!</i>

01:22.875 --> 01:25.458
<i>(ALL SHRIEK)</i>

01:25.500 --> 01:28.875
<i>No, no, no. It's all wrong!</i>
<i>The ponies are all supposed</i>

01:28.916 --> 01:30.291
<i>to get along, remember?</i>

01:30.333 --> 01:31.708
<i>Boring!</i>

01:31.750 --> 01:35.708
<i>It's like in the olden times when</i>
<i>all three ponykinds were friends.</i>

01:35.750 --> 01:37.500
<i>Uhh! Here we go again.</i>

01:37.541 --> 01:40.416
<i>And they never used their magic</i>
<i>against each other.</i>

01:40.458 --> 01:42.583
<i>- You're wrong.</i>
<i>- No, I'm not!</i>

01:42.625 --> 01:45.625
<i>My mom says the pegasi and unicorns</i>
<i>tried to eat up all the earth ponies</i>

01:45.666 --> 01:47.916
<i>by zapping 'em with lasers</i>
<i>and frying 'em to a crisp.</i>

01:47.958 --> 01:49.708
<i>They wouldn't do that.</i>

01:49.750 --> 01:52.250
<i>So the earth ponies kicked</i>
<i>their butts in an epic battle.</i>

01:52.291 --> 01:54.291
<i>And if they ever try to come back</i>
<i>to Maretime Bay,</i>

01:54.333 --> 01:55.791
<i>we'll kick their butts again!</i>

01:55.833 --> 01:58.500
<i>Those are lies. Hitch, tell him.</i>

01:58.541 --> 02:02.750
<i>Well, that is kind of what our</i>
<i>teacher said in history class, but...</i>

02:02.791 --> 02:05.250
<i>But, hey, we can play the game</i>
<i>your way if you want, Sunny.</i>

02:05.291 --> 02:06.791
<i>- I don't mind.</i>
<i>- Well, I do.</i>

02:06.833 --> 02:10.541
<i>It's a boring game. Let's play</i>
<i>Pegasus Barbecue instead!</i>

02:10.583 --> 02:11.791
<i>Sprout, stop it!</i>

02:11.833 --> 02:14.500
<i>- SPROUT: Earth pony burgers!</i>
<i>- I'm going to tell my dad!</i>

02:21.291 --> 02:23.750
<i>(CLOCK TICKS QUIETLY)</i>

02:27.875 --> 02:29.625
<i>- Horn fight!</i>
<i>- You're going to break them!</i>

02:29.666 --> 02:31.208
<i>Take that, earth pony! Pew, pew!</i>

02:31.250 --> 02:33.875
<i>Dad, tell them</i>
<i>that's not what they do.</i>

02:33.916 --> 02:36.500
<i>Time to head on home,</i>
<i>don't you think, colts?</i>

02:36.541 --> 02:38.625
<i>Uhh! Fine!</i>

02:38.666 --> 02:40.208
<i>Pew, pew!</i>

02:40.250 --> 02:42.583
<i>Oh, no! My brains are melting!</i>

02:42.625 --> 02:43.833
<i>(DOOR CREAKS OPEN)</i>

02:43.875 --> 02:45.541
<i>- Mom?</i>
<i>- Hello, Mrs Cloverleaf.</i>

02:45.583 --> 02:49.208
<i>How many times have I told you?</i>
<i>You cannot just go trotting off</i>

02:49.250 --> 02:52.291
<i>without my permission,</i>
<i>especially not here.</i>

02:52.333 --> 02:54.666
<i>And why is that again, Phyllis?</i>

02:54.708 --> 02:56.916
<i>Because you are brainwashing</i>
<i>their minds</i>

02:56.958 --> 02:58.875
<i>with all of your...nonsense.</i>

02:58.916 --> 03:00.541
<i>It's called research, Phyllis.</i>

03:00.583 --> 03:03.250
<i>And by the way,</i>
<i>I leave all the brainwashing</i>

03:03.291 --> 03:04.875
<i>in Maretime Bay to you.</i>

03:04.916 --> 03:05.916
<i>Unicorn cupcake?</i>

03:05.958 --> 03:08.375
<i>Freshly baked.</i>

03:08.416 --> 03:11.166
<i>Uhh! You know,</i>
<i>you're an earth pony, Argyle.</i>

03:11.208 --> 03:15.208
<i>You should really start acting</i>
<i>like one, at least for her sake.</i>

03:15.250 --> 03:16.666
<i>(GIGGLES)</i>

03:18.416 --> 03:20.666
<i>PHYLLIS: Who does he think he is,</i>
<i>talking to me like that?</i>

03:20.708 --> 03:22.375
<i>That pony is trouble!</i>

03:22.416 --> 03:24.791
<i>Don't worry, Mommy.</i>
<i>When I become sheriff,</i>

03:24.833 --> 03:26.958
<i>I'll keep everypony in line.</i>

03:27.000 --> 03:31.375
<i>Hmm...Sheriff Sprout. Oh,</i>
<i>it does have a certain ring to it.</i>

03:35.541 --> 03:36.750
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

03:36.791 --> 03:38.458
<i>What's the matter, Sunny Bunny?</i>

03:38.500 --> 03:41.000
<i>Hitch and Sprout</i>
<i>still don't believe me.</i>

03:41.041 --> 03:42.625
<i>Maybe one day they will.</i>

03:42.666 --> 03:45.833
<i>But the important thing is that</i>
<i>you stand up for what you believe in.</i>

03:45.875 --> 03:46.958
<i>OK?</i>

03:47.000 --> 03:51.541
<i>Well, when I grow up, I'm going to</i>
<i>show everypony that we are right.</i>

03:51.583 --> 03:53.208
<i>- Oh?</i>
<i>- Yeah.</i>

03:53.250 --> 03:57.875
<i>And someday the both of us</i>
<i>will meet unicorns or a pegasus</i>

03:57.916 --> 04:00.166
<i>and we'll be best friends forever!</i>

04:00.208 --> 04:02.666
<i>Well, maybe today is that day.</i>

04:02.708 --> 04:03.875
<i>Look, a unicorn!</i>

04:03.916 --> 04:05.875
<i>(GASPS) Where? Where?</i>

04:05.916 --> 04:07.000
<i>Over here.</i>

04:08.708 --> 04:11.000
<i>(LAUGHTER)</i>

04:12.125 --> 04:14.083
<i>- Hold on.</i>
<i>- Whee!</i>

04:14.125 --> 04:16.541
<i>- I'm soaring through the sky!</i>
<i>- Yee-ha!</i>

04:16.583 --> 04:18.750
<i>Wait. Dad, I have an idea!</i>

04:24.791 --> 04:27.833
<i>(CLEARS THROAT)</i>
<i>"Dear unicorns and pegasi,</i>

04:27.875 --> 04:30.833
<i>"you have friends in Maretime Bay.</i>
<i>Come visit us."</i>

04:30.875 --> 04:32.083
<i>Can we send it?</i>

04:32.125 --> 04:34.083
<i>DAD: I think it's our duty.</i>

04:51.500 --> 04:53.375
<i>(GIGGLES)</i>

04:53.416 --> 04:55.791
<i>- Can you tell me the story?</i>
<i>- Again?</i>

04:55.833 --> 04:59.041
<i>- Please.</i>
<i>- (CHUCKLES)</i>

04:59.083 --> 05:03.416
<i>Once upon a time, many, many moons</i>
<i>ago, in ancient Equestria,</i>

05:03.458 --> 05:06.083
<i>- there lived a very special...</i>
<i>- Unicorn!</i>

05:06.125 --> 05:07.833
<i>(DAD CHUCKLES)</i>

05:07.875 --> 05:10.125
<i>DAD: The unicorn was very bright...</i>

05:10.166 --> 05:11.875
<i>SUNNY: As bright as the sun.</i>

05:11.916 --> 05:14.458
<i>DAD: One day, the princess</i>
<i>summoned her to the castle</i>

05:14.500 --> 05:15.958
<i>for an important assignment.</i>

05:16.000 --> 05:18.250
<i>- To learn about friendship!</i>
<i>- Mm-hm.</i>

05:18.291 --> 05:20.666
<i>She soon made lots of new friends.</i>

05:20.708 --> 05:23.958
<i>SUNNY: Earth ponies, pegasuses</i>
<i>and unicorns.</i>

05:24.000 --> 05:27.750
<i>Together, they showed everypony</i>
<i>the magic of friendship</i>

05:27.791 --> 05:29.000
<i>and how to live in harmony.</i>

05:29.041 --> 05:31.416
<i>Wow. You finished it.</i>

05:31.458 --> 05:33.458
<i>Pretty neat, huh?</i>

05:33.500 --> 05:35.125
<i>Earth ponies watched in wonder</i>

05:35.166 --> 05:38.041
<i>as pegasi painted rainbows</i>
<i>across the sky.</i>

05:38.083 --> 05:42.208
<i>The nights were lit up</i>
<i>by 100 unicorn horns.</i>

05:42.250 --> 05:43.666
<i>It's beautiful.</i>

05:45.750 --> 05:50.250
<i>I wish I had a friend</i>
<i>who could fly around or float things.</i>

05:50.291 --> 05:52.250
<i>(YAWNS)</i>

05:52.291 --> 05:55.416
<i>Why can't we be friends any more?</i>

05:55.458 --> 05:59.041
<i>(SIGHS) That, my darling,</i>
<i>is a big question,</i>

05:59.083 --> 06:03.458
<i>and maybe one day,</i>
<i>we'll figure it out together.</i>

06:03.500 --> 06:04.708
<i>We'll do our part...</i>

06:04.750 --> 06:06.208
<i>BOTH: Hoof to heart.</i>

06:08.958 --> 06:11.083
<i>Goodnight, Daddy.</i>

06:11.125 --> 06:12.791
<i>Goodnight, my little pony.</i>

06:16.625 --> 06:18.708
<i>Goodnight, friends.</i>

06:25.458 --> 06:27.916
<i>(SNORES)</i>

06:30.666 --> 06:32.500
<i>(ALARM CLOCK BEEPS)</i>

06:34.291 --> 06:35.875
<i>(YAWNS)</i>

06:42.041 --> 06:43.208
<i>(SNORTS)</i>

06:56.750 --> 06:58.000
<i>Perfect.</i>

07:13.083 --> 07:16.416
<i>Today's the day, Dad.</i>
<i>I actually have a plan this time.</i>

07:16.458 --> 07:17.625
<i>Wish me luck!</i>

07:24.375 --> 07:26.083
<i># Good morning, sun</i>

07:26.125 --> 07:28.083
<i># No time to chat, I gotta run</i>

07:28.125 --> 07:30.291
<i># Cos I got places to be</i>

07:31.375 --> 07:32.625
<i># So much to do</i>

07:32.666 --> 07:34.833
<i># Excited, yes, and nervous too</i>

07:34.875 --> 07:37.750
<i># A change is starting with me</i>

07:37.791 --> 07:41.083
<i># I never worry 'bout</i>
<i>upsetting carts, hardened hearts</i>

07:41.125 --> 07:43.541
<i># Or wonder, "Will I belong?"</i>

07:43.583 --> 07:45.208
<i># I’ve heard it enough!</i>

07:45.250 --> 07:46.958
<i># I’m calling their bluff</i>

07:47.000 --> 07:50.333
<i># I’ll never get lost in the grey!</i>

07:50.375 --> 07:53.625
<i># There’s something inside</i>
<i>burns bigger than pride</i>

07:53.666 --> 07:56.916
<i># Shines out of me, lighting the way</i>

07:56.958 --> 07:59.125
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

07:59.166 --> 08:00.416
<i># Be my day</i>

08:00.458 --> 08:03.041
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

08:03.083 --> 08:05.375
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

08:05.416 --> 08:07.458
<i># Gonna be my day!</i>

08:07.500 --> 08:09.208
<i># Gonna be my day</i>

08:10.375 --> 08:11.541
<i># Hey there, hello</i>

08:11.583 --> 08:13.291
<i># The friends I make</i>
<i>The friends I know</i>

08:13.333 --> 08:16.083
<i># Today you answer my call</i>

08:16.125 --> 08:19.833
<i># Instead of hide</i>
<i>Instead of staying stuck inside</i>

08:19.875 --> 08:23.125
<i># Instead of building your wall</i>

08:23.166 --> 08:24.541
<i># Come on and party with me</i>

08:24.583 --> 08:25.583
<i># Join the band</i>

08:25.625 --> 08:26.625
<i># Understand</i>

08:26.666 --> 08:28.875
<i># We'll all be singing the song</i>

08:28.916 --> 08:30.791
<i># I’ve heard it enough!</i>

08:30.833 --> 08:32.083
<i># I’m calling their bluff!</i>

08:32.125 --> 08:35.333
<i># I’ll never get lost in the grey!</i>

08:35.375 --> 08:36.833
<i># Go big or go home!</i>

08:36.875 --> 08:38.583
<i># Get real or get known!</i>

08:38.625 --> 08:42.291
<i># Get ready and raring to say...</i>

08:42.333 --> 08:44.208
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

08:44.250 --> 08:45.791
<i># Be my day!</i>

08:45.833 --> 08:48.666
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

08:48.708 --> 08:50.583
<i># Everyone’s afraid</i>

08:50.625 --> 08:51.625
<i>(ALL SHRIEK)</i>

08:51.666 --> 08:53.333
<i># Always judging</i>

08:53.375 --> 08:55.166
<i># Never budging</i>

08:55.208 --> 09:01.375
<i># Ain’t it time we made the team</i>

09:01.416 --> 09:03.333
<i># The dream?</i>

09:03.375 --> 09:06.208
<i># Oh...</i>

09:06.250 --> 09:07.708
<i># Let’s open our eyes</i>

09:07.750 --> 09:09.458
<i># Sun starting to rise</i>

09:09.500 --> 09:12.958
<i># And finally able to say...</i>

09:13.000 --> 09:15.208
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

09:15.250 --> 09:16.625
<i># Gonna be my day!</i>

09:16.666 --> 09:18.333
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

09:18.375 --> 09:19.833
<i># Gonna be my day!</i>

09:19.875 --> 09:21.666
<i># Gonna be, gonna be, gonna be</i>
<i>my day</i>

09:21.708 --> 09:23.291
<i># Be my day! #</i>

09:28.291 --> 09:30.083
<i>Aha, there you are, Sunny.</i>

09:30.125 --> 09:32.166
<i>Just the pony I was expecting.</i>

09:32.208 --> 09:33.666
<i>Morning, Sheriff Hitch.</i>

09:33.708 --> 09:35.625
<i>I see you brought the whole squad</i>
<i>along again.</i>

09:35.666 --> 09:36.916
<i>(ALL SQUEAK)</i>

09:36.958 --> 09:39.708
<i>(SIGHS) What is it with me and</i>
<i>critters? I'm like a magnet to them.</i>

09:39.750 --> 09:42.791
<i>Guys, come on.</i>
<i>Give Hitch a little space.</i>

09:42.833 --> 09:44.375
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

09:44.416 --> 09:46.958
<i>- So, what's up?</i>
<i>- Oh, please, like you don't know.</i>

09:47.000 --> 09:49.583
<i>Today is the annual presentation</i>
<i>at Canterlogic.</i>

09:49.625 --> 09:51.875
<i>- Hey, I'm headed there right now.</i>
<i>- No, you're not.</i>

09:51.916 --> 09:55.666
<i>Listen, I know that you have come up</i>
<i>with some hare-brained scheme</i>

09:55.708 --> 09:58.000
<i>to sabotage it, and if you think</i>
<i>I'm just going to let you walk in...</i>

09:58.041 --> 09:59.666
<i>Hey, Hitch...</i>

09:59.708 --> 10:01.791
<i>- No.</i>
<i>- Come on.</i>

10:01.833 --> 10:03.500
<i>Good morning, Sheriff Hitch.</i>

10:03.541 --> 10:05.625
<i>Morning, Mayflower. Dahlia.</i>
<i>(CHUCKLES)</i>

10:05.666 --> 10:07.500
<i>Sunny, I'm on duty.</i>

10:08.750 --> 10:10.291
<i>(GROANS)</i>

10:10.333 --> 10:12.333
<i>BOTH: Up high! Down low!</i>
<i>Hitch it to a post!</i>

10:12.375 --> 10:15.250
<i>Flip it sunny side up</i>
<i>and on a piece of toast!</i>

10:15.291 --> 10:16.958
<i>OK?</i>

10:17.000 --> 10:19.250
<i>(GASPING) I did what you asked for,</i>
<i>Hitch.</i>

10:19.291 --> 10:22.375
<i>She never left my side,</i>
<i>not even once.</i>

10:22.416 --> 10:25.666
<i>Oh, hey, Sprout. You OK?</i>
<i>You seem kind of wheezy.</i>

10:25.708 --> 10:28.125
<i>That's Deputy Sprout to you.</i>

10:28.166 --> 10:30.416
<i>Hey, wait up! I'm not finished!</i>

10:30.458 --> 10:33.583
<i>Sunny! Sunny, we both know</i>
<i>how this goes.</i>

10:33.625 --> 10:37.000
<i>Every year you try to sneak in</i>
<i>and every year I stop you.</i>

10:37.041 --> 10:39.458
<i>Look, you have nothing</i>
<i>to worry about.</i>

10:39.500 --> 10:42.041
<i>I'll just go into the factory,</i>
<i>deliver my smoothies...</i>

10:42.083 --> 10:44.666
<i>Uh-uh. You can't even step</i>
<i>a hoof in there.</i>

10:44.708 --> 10:46.125
<i>My mom had you banned.</i>

10:46.166 --> 10:47.541
<i>- But I...</i>
<i>- (SIGHS)</i>

10:47.583 --> 10:50.000
<i>I'm asking you as your friend, Sunny,</i>
<i>not as sheriff.</i>

10:50.041 --> 10:52.708
<i>Just please try not to pull</i>
<i>any stunts today.</i>

10:52.750 --> 10:54.750
<i>OK. OK.</i>

10:54.791 --> 10:56.500
<i>I'll try.</i>

10:56.541 --> 10:57.583
<i>Thank you.</i>

10:57.625 --> 11:00.833
<i>Now, give your delivery to Sprout</i>
<i>and go home.</i>

11:01.958 --> 11:05.000
<i>Hey. Hey!</i>
<i>That's a violation of Code 33.</i>

11:06.666 --> 11:08.708
<i>Bye-bye.</i>

11:08.750 --> 11:09.958
<i>(LAUGHS)</i>

11:18.333 --> 11:20.208
<i>Hey, watch it!</i>

11:20.250 --> 11:24.291
<i>Welcome, everypony. Got any questions</i>
<i>about the Canterlogic factory?</i>

11:24.333 --> 11:26.083
<i>Happy to answer them.</i>

11:26.125 --> 11:27.708
<i>MARE: Where are the free smoothies?</i>

11:36.041 --> 11:38.333
<i>(SIGHS) You know what, Sprout?</i>

11:38.375 --> 11:41.166
<i>I think I finally got through</i>
<i>to Sunny.</i>

11:42.458 --> 11:44.875
<i>ANNOUNCER: It's the moment</i>
<i>you've all been waiting for.</i>

11:44.916 --> 11:46.250
<i>As the founder of Canterlogic,</i>

11:46.291 --> 11:49.833
<i>she's been keeping us safe</i>
<i>and stylish for the last 20 moons.</i>

11:49.875 --> 11:54.291
<i>Please go wild for the one and only</i>
<i>Phyllis Cloverleaf!</i>

11:54.333 --> 11:56.250
<i>- (APPLAUSE)</i>
<i>- Thank you. Thank you.</i>

11:56.291 --> 11:59.375
<i>How are you? Thank you so much.</i>

11:59.416 --> 12:03.250
<i>We here at Canterlogic</i>
<i>are so thrilled</i>

12:03.291 --> 12:07.791
<i>to create perfect products</i>
<i>that protect ponies like you...</i>

12:07.833 --> 12:10.166
<i>...from ponies like that.</i>

12:10.208 --> 12:11.541
<i>(BOOING)</i>

12:11.583 --> 12:14.208
<i>And like I always say,</i>

12:14.250 --> 12:16.375
<i>to be scared is...</i>

12:16.416 --> 12:18.416
<i>ALL: To be prepared!</i>

12:18.458 --> 12:21.250
<i>Oh, I love it. That's right.</i>

12:21.291 --> 12:24.500
<i>- Ya-hoo!</i>
<i>- So let's start the show!</i>

12:24.541 --> 12:25.875
<i>(MUSIC)</i>

12:25.916 --> 12:28.625
<i>Up first, we have Sugar Moonlight</i>

12:28.666 --> 12:30.583
<i>looking absolutely stunning</i>

12:30.625 --> 12:33.916
<i>in our high-tech</i>
<i>Anti-Mind-Reading Hat.</i>

12:33.958 --> 12:37.375
<i>All those psychic unicorns out there</i>
<i>are going to be out of luck</i>

12:37.416 --> 12:38.833
<i>when you wear this little number!</i>

12:38.875 --> 12:41.791
<i>Now let's welcome Sparkle Chaser</i>

12:41.833 --> 12:44.208
<i>in his Pega-Periscope Goggles -</i>

12:44.250 --> 12:48.541
<i>the easy way to keep</i>
<i>your eye on the sky.</i>

12:48.583 --> 12:50.083
<i>Oh!</i>

12:50.125 --> 12:52.208
<i>It's all part of the show!</i>

12:52.250 --> 12:56.500
<i>Next up, the Earth Pony</i>
<i>Balloon Escape Pack.</i>

12:58.125 --> 12:59.750
<i>Whoa...</i>

12:59.791 --> 13:01.458
<i>Uh... Whoa!</i>

13:01.500 --> 13:03.458
<i>Argh! Arghhh!</i>

13:03.500 --> 13:05.708
<i>Yikes. That's going to be</i>
<i>a lot of paperwork.</i>

13:05.750 --> 13:08.333
<i>We take great care</i>
<i>here at Canterlogic</i>

13:08.375 --> 13:11.666
<i>to ensure the safety of you,</i>
<i>our loyal customers.</i>

13:11.708 --> 13:13.458
<i>ALL: Aww!</i>

13:13.500 --> 13:15.208
<i>Now, please, stand back.</i>

13:15.250 --> 13:18.583
<i>This product-testing demonstration</i>
<i>is fully automated.</i>

13:22.291 --> 13:24.583
<i>(GASPS)</i>

13:24.625 --> 13:26.833
<i>Earth ponies of Maretime Bay,</i>

13:26.875 --> 13:29.333
<i>fear is not your friend!</i>

13:29.375 --> 13:32.625
<i>But the unicorns</i>
<i>and pegasi can be.</i>

13:32.666 --> 13:35.083
<i>Let's extend the hoof of friendship.</i>

13:36.333 --> 13:38.208
<i>That is not what I meant.</i>

13:38.250 --> 13:40.500
<i>Turn it off, turn it off!</i>

13:40.541 --> 13:44.291
<i>So now you can prevent</i>
<i>an aerial abduction</i>

13:44.333 --> 13:47.583
<i>with a set of our new</i>
<i>Anti-Pegalift Boots!</i>

13:47.625 --> 13:51.625
<i>Peace with pegasi!</i>
<i>Unity with unicorns!</i>

13:52.833 --> 13:55.166
<i>Whoa! Give me that back!</i>

13:55.208 --> 13:56.375
<i>(SIGHS) Sunny!</i>

13:56.416 --> 13:59.458
<i>Peace with...pegasi!</i>

13:59.500 --> 14:05.500
<i>Uh...everypony take a look at</i>
<i>our Unicorn Entrapment Device.</i>

14:05.541 --> 14:07.541
<i>Whoa!</i>

14:07.583 --> 14:09.416
<i>Toots, Sweets, shut her down!</i>

14:09.458 --> 14:11.083
<i>- Sheriff's orders!</i>
<i>- We're trying.</i>

14:11.125 --> 14:13.583
<i>Fully automated means</i>
<i>it has to go through the whole cycle.</i>

14:19.125 --> 14:20.875
<i>Oh, no. Ooh!</i>

14:22.583 --> 14:25.708
<i>Peace with pegasi!</i>
<i>Unity with unicorns!</i>

14:25.750 --> 14:29.208
<i>PHYLLIS: And this</i>
<i>is the Splat-a-pult!</i>

14:29.250 --> 14:31.083
<i>Ohhh!</i>

14:31.125 --> 14:33.375
<i>Cease fire!</i>

14:33.416 --> 14:34.458
<i>ALL: Ooh.</i>

14:34.500 --> 14:37.291
<i>PHYLLIS: Let's hear it, everypony.</i>
<i>Come on!</i>

14:40.458 --> 14:42.708
<i>Uh...</i>

14:46.250 --> 14:47.500
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

14:47.541 --> 14:50.250
<i>(PANTS)</i>

14:50.291 --> 14:54.583
<i>Aren't you tired of being scared</i>
<i>all the time?</i>

14:54.625 --> 14:57.666
<i>The truth is, we're not in danger.</i>

14:57.708 --> 14:59.625
<i>It's all a lie.</i>

14:59.666 --> 15:03.125
<i>We don't need any</i>
<i>of this Canterlogic junk.</i>

15:03.166 --> 15:04.958
<i>Oh, we don't, do we?</i>

15:05.000 --> 15:09.875
<i>How do you suggest that we defend</i>
<i>ourselves? With hugs and cupcakes?</i>

15:09.916 --> 15:11.166
<i>(LAUGHTER)</i>

15:12.625 --> 15:14.666
<i>Just imagine...if you had</i>

15:14.708 --> 15:17.250
<i>a friend who could fly</i>

15:17.291 --> 15:18.666
<i>or a friend who could...</i>

15:18.708 --> 15:20.541
<i>Fry your brains</i>
<i>with a single horn zap?</i>

15:20.583 --> 15:23.041
<i>Or swoop down and snatch you away?</i>

15:23.083 --> 15:24.916
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

15:24.958 --> 15:26.291
<i>Sheriff, do your job.</i>

15:26.333 --> 15:28.041
<i>All right, Sunny, let's go.</i>

15:28.083 --> 15:31.375
<i>No. Everypony needs to hear this.</i>

15:31.416 --> 15:35.750
<i>Everything you believe about</i>
<i>pegasi and unicorns is wrong.</i>

15:35.791 --> 15:38.208
<i>They used to be our friends</i>

15:38.250 --> 15:39.958
<i>and can be again.</i>

15:40.000 --> 15:42.833
<i>AUDIENCE MEMBER: Hey, we don't need</i>
<i>any of them round here!</i>

15:42.875 --> 15:44.666
<i>Come on, let's go.</i>
<i>Show's over, Sunny.</i>

15:44.708 --> 15:47.250
<i>AUDIENCE MEMBER: Sunny,</i>
<i>you're just embarrassing yourself!</i>

15:47.291 --> 15:48.833
<i>PHYLLIS: It's quite sad, really.</i>

15:48.875 --> 15:50.750
<i>Now, where were we?</i>

15:52.000 --> 15:55.708
<i>Do you have any idea how many</i>
<i>bylaws you broke in there?</i>

15:55.750 --> 15:57.541
<i>I'm sure you're about to tell me.</i>

15:57.583 --> 16:00.916
<i>Actually, for once I can't,</i>
<i>because there's so many!</i>

16:00.958 --> 16:04.708
<i>I tried to warn you. I can't keep</i>
<i>associating with some pony</i>

16:04.750 --> 16:07.500
<i>who breaks every rule and</i>
<i>causes chaos wherever she goes.</i>

16:07.541 --> 16:08.666
<i>I'm the sheriff!</i>

16:08.708 --> 16:12.458
<i>Exactly. Other ponies</i>
<i>look up to you. You can help.</i>

16:13.833 --> 16:15.583
<i>The law is the law, Sunny,</i>

16:15.625 --> 16:18.208
<i>and I'm here to uphold it</i>
<i>and keep everypony safe.</i>

16:18.250 --> 16:20.416
<i>Aha, you just said everypony.</i>

16:20.458 --> 16:22.708
<i>That includes pegasi and unicorns.</i>

16:22.750 --> 16:25.208
<i>Come on, Sunny, what did you think</i>
<i>was gonna happen?</i>

16:25.250 --> 16:27.166
<i>You give a little speech and what?</i>

16:27.208 --> 16:29.791
<i>Everypony just magically welcomes</i>
<i>unicorns and pegasi</i>

16:29.833 --> 16:31.291
<i>into Maretime Bay?</i>

16:31.333 --> 16:34.083
<i>You keep saying there's nothing to be</i>
<i>afraid of. Well, then, prove it.</i>

16:35.583 --> 16:39.250
<i>(SIGHS) All of that pony unity stuff</i>

16:39.291 --> 16:42.833
<i>was just a foal's bedtime story</i>
<i>made up by your dad.</i>

16:42.875 --> 16:46.333
<i>Like it or not, this is the way</i>
<i>it is, and always will be.</i>

16:49.250 --> 16:51.583
<i>I'm the last real friend</i>
<i>you got in this town.</i>

16:51.625 --> 16:53.208
<i>You really want to lose me too?</i>

16:54.333 --> 16:56.333
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

17:05.083 --> 17:06.958
<i>(GIGGLING)</i>

17:14.666 --> 17:16.291
<i>- Rarrgh!</i>
<i>- Argh!</i>

17:16.333 --> 17:18.125
<i>(GIGGLING)</i>

17:18.166 --> 17:20.041
<i>- Rarrgh!</i>
<i>- (GIGGLING)</i>

17:27.458 --> 17:29.291
<i>I wish you were here, Dad.</i>

17:39.875 --> 17:41.791
<i>(GALLOPING)</i>

17:41.833 --> 17:43.500
<i>Uh...argh!</i>

17:43.541 --> 17:45.916
<i>(SHRIEKING)</i>

17:47.041 --> 17:48.541
<i>What the...?</i>

17:50.375 --> 17:52.375
<i>What's going on? What's happening?</i>

17:55.791 --> 17:57.416
<i>(SQUEAKS)</i>

17:58.416 --> 17:59.666
<i>Argh!</i>

17:59.708 --> 18:01.333
<i>(BRAKES SCREECH)</i>

18:04.208 --> 18:06.000
<i>(GASPS)</i>

18:06.041 --> 18:08.791
<i>Hi, new friend! My name's Izzy.</i>

18:11.416 --> 18:12.416
<i>U...U...</i>

18:12.458 --> 18:13.958
<i>Unicorn!</i>

18:14.000 --> 18:16.708
<i>(SHRIEKING)</i>

18:19.541 --> 18:21.791
<i>Ooh, is everypony</i>
<i>playing hide-and-seek?</i>

18:21.833 --> 18:22.833
<i>I see you!</i>

18:22.875 --> 18:24.833
<i>Argh! It's a unicorn!</i>

18:26.791 --> 18:28.625
<i>Hey, what's going on?</i>

18:28.666 --> 18:31.083
<i>(GASPS)</i>

18:31.125 --> 18:33.500
<i>Unicorn attack!</i>

18:33.541 --> 18:35.375
<i>- (ALARM BLARES)</i>
<i>- This is not a drill!</i>

18:35.416 --> 18:37.916
<i>I repeat, this is not a drill!</i>

18:40.958 --> 18:42.833
<i>A vulnerable young pony.</i>

18:45.458 --> 18:47.416
<i>Your son is safe now, ma'am.</i>

18:48.583 --> 18:50.875
<i>- This isn't my kid!</i>
<i>- You're welcome.</i>

18:50.916 --> 18:53.666
<i>Man the Splat-a-pult!</i>
<i>Activate the unicorn trap!</i>

18:53.708 --> 18:55.791
<i>Pick up that litter!</i>

18:58.791 --> 19:00.166
<i>Wow.</i>

19:00.208 --> 19:01.500
<i>Is that the sea?</i>

19:01.541 --> 19:02.750
<i>I've never seen the sea.</i>

19:05.375 --> 19:07.416
<i>- (ALARM BLARES)</i>
<i>- I've got to get you of here!</i>

19:07.458 --> 19:10.375
<i>Earth ponies are serious about games.</i>

19:10.416 --> 19:13.000
<i>They're not playing,</i>
<i>they're terrified.</i>

19:13.041 --> 19:16.166
<i>- Oh, no. Of what?</i>
<i>- You! You're a unicorn.</i>

19:16.208 --> 19:17.583
<i>Earth ponies hate unicorns.</i>

19:17.625 --> 19:19.625
<i>Really? That seems a little harsh.</i>

19:23.916 --> 19:25.208
<i>Let's go!</i>

19:40.291 --> 19:42.625
<i>(HUMS)</i>

19:47.041 --> 19:49.250
<i>Oh, I haven't seen this one yet.</i>

19:49.291 --> 19:51.083
<i>(ALARM BLARES)</i>

19:51.125 --> 19:52.291
<i>(GASPS)</i>

19:54.666 --> 19:56.583
<i>All right, citizens, calm down.</i>

19:56.625 --> 19:58.375
<i>The threat has been neutralised.</i>

19:58.416 --> 20:00.083
<i>The unicorn has been captured.</i>

20:00.125 --> 20:01.250
<i>You may now cheer.</i>

20:01.291 --> 20:02.791
<i>(CHEERING)</i>

20:04.458 --> 20:05.458
<i>Sunny!</i>

20:08.916 --> 20:10.708
<i>What are you doing?</i>

20:13.125 --> 20:14.583
<i>Don't even think about it.</i>

20:17.208 --> 20:19.916
<i>No, don't you dare.</i>
<i>No, no, no, no. Sunny!</i>

20:19.958 --> 20:22.541
<i>So, your name's Sunny?</i>

20:22.583 --> 20:24.750
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

20:24.791 --> 20:26.000
<i>Argh!</i>

20:27.666 --> 20:30.208
<i>Bye! It was nice to meet you all!</i>

20:30.250 --> 20:32.416
<i>Deputy, to the lighthouse!</i>

20:32.458 --> 20:33.791
<i>Uh...</i>

20:35.666 --> 20:40.458
<i>- Oh, no, I appear to be trapped.</i>
<i>- (SIGHS) You gotta be kidding me.</i>

20:59.458 --> 21:03.125
<i>Do earth ponies</i>
<i>also like staring contests?</i>

21:03.166 --> 21:06.833
<i>Hmm!</i>

21:06.875 --> 21:09.083
<i>You win. I blinked.</i>

21:09.125 --> 21:11.958
<i>There's a unicorn in my house.</i>

21:12.000 --> 21:13.333
<i>This is so cool!</i>

21:13.375 --> 21:16.458
<i>Wait, no, it's bad, very, very bad.</i>
<i>What have I done?</i>

21:16.500 --> 21:20.416
<i>Wow! I've never seen</i>
<i>an earth pony before.</i>

21:20.458 --> 21:24.458
<i>We look exactly the same,</i>
<i>except for this, of course.</i>

21:24.500 --> 21:26.625
<i>Oh, hey, be careful</i>
<i>where you point that thing.</i>

21:26.666 --> 21:28.875
<i>- Why?</i>
<i>- Well, I...um...</i>

21:28.916 --> 21:31.833
<i>...sort of don't want to get zapped</i>
<i>with a wayward laser beam,</i>

21:31.875 --> 21:33.833
<i>but of course you know that already.</i>

21:33.875 --> 21:36.208
<i>You've probably been reading</i>
<i>my mind this whole time.</i>

21:36.250 --> 21:38.625
<i>Isn't it supposed to glow,</i>
<i>by the way,</i>

21:38.666 --> 21:41.250
<i>or does that only happen</i>
<i>when you levitate stuff?</i>

21:41.291 --> 21:43.000
<i>Well, actually...</i>

21:43.041 --> 21:45.625
<i>Wait, don't answer that yet.</i>
<i>Let me get my notebook.</i>

21:45.666 --> 21:47.458
<i>OK. Wow.</i>

21:47.500 --> 21:50.291
<i>OK, 142 questions for a unicorn.</i>

21:50.333 --> 21:51.916
<i>Question number one.</i>
<i>Where do you live?</i>

21:51.958 --> 21:53.916
<i>- Bridlewood.</i>
<i>- I knew it.</i>

21:53.958 --> 21:55.416
<i>Do unicorns really live in trees?</i>

21:55.458 --> 21:57.916
<i>Do they eat pizza?</i>
<i>If so, what toppings do they like?</i>

21:57.958 --> 21:59.416
<i>If not, why not?</i>

21:59.458 --> 22:01.958
<i>Can you actually fry pony brains</i>
<i>with a single horn zap?</i>

22:02.000 --> 22:03.666
<i>(GASPS) Can you make this float?</i>

22:05.208 --> 22:07.750
<i>No, but I can do this.</i>

22:11.875 --> 22:13.541
<i>Ta-da!</i>

22:15.541 --> 22:17.583
<i>Wait, you don't have any magic?</i>

22:17.625 --> 22:19.583
<i>- HITCH: Sunny Starscout!</i>
<i>- (FEEDBACK WHINES)</i>

22:19.625 --> 22:20.708
<i>Argh, that hurt.</i>

22:20.750 --> 22:24.541
<i>Sunny Starscout, I know</i>
<i>you're in there with that unicorn.</i>

22:24.583 --> 22:27.250
<i>Come out with your hooves up</i>
<i>and surrender.</i>

22:27.291 --> 22:30.166
<i>Yeah, you're completely surrounded.</i>

22:32.166 --> 22:33.625
<i>Will you let me do my job?</i>

22:33.666 --> 22:36.000
<i>- You are under arrest.</i>
<i>- This is bad.</i>

22:36.041 --> 22:38.750
<i>- How sneaky are you?</i>
<i>- Er, medium sneaky.</i>

22:38.791 --> 22:40.958
<i>I can work with that.</i>
<i>OK, I'll distract them.</i>

22:41.000 --> 22:42.625
<i>Pff! Relax!</i>

22:42.666 --> 22:44.833
<i>- I'll talk to him.</i>
<i>- No, no!</i>

22:44.875 --> 22:46.333
<i>Hi, guys.</i>

22:46.375 --> 22:48.875
<i>Now, I know what you're thinking.</i>

22:48.916 --> 22:50.875
<i>Argh! She's already reading</i>
<i>our minds!</i>

22:50.916 --> 22:52.916
<i>Quick, before she fries our brains!</i>

22:52.958 --> 22:54.916
<i>What are you doing?</i>
<i>Where are you going?</i>

22:54.958 --> 22:57.375
<i>- To get reinforcements!</i>
<i>- We have reinforcements?</i>

22:57.416 --> 22:58.458
<i>Huh?</i>

22:58.500 --> 23:00.000
<i>Oh, come on!</i>

23:04.750 --> 23:07.250
<i>- You don't have any magic?</i>
<i>- No.</i>

23:07.291 --> 23:09.250
<i>(GASPS)</i>

23:09.291 --> 23:11.291
<i>No magic?</i>

23:11.333 --> 23:14.208
<i>If it makes you feel any better,</i>
<i>we did have it,</i>

23:14.250 --> 23:17.125
<i>but that was many, many,</i>
<i>many moons ago.</i>

23:17.166 --> 23:18.875
<i>It just, poof, disappeared.</i>

23:18.916 --> 23:21.541
<i>Everypony thinks the pesky pegasi</i>
<i>had something to do with it,</i>

23:21.583 --> 23:23.125
<i>but, oh... Oh, hey,</i>

23:23.166 --> 23:26.250
<i>you look kind of woozy.</i>
<i>Are you OK?</i>

23:26.291 --> 23:30.958
<i>Huh... I am on the run with a unicorn</i>
<i>who has no magic.</i>

23:31.000 --> 23:32.708
<i>What are we going to do?</i>

23:32.750 --> 23:34.125
<i>(SNIFFS)</i>

23:35.500 --> 23:37.083
<i>What are you doing?</i>

23:37.125 --> 23:39.291
<i>- You don't smell.</i>
<i>- Thanks. Wait, what?</i>

23:39.333 --> 23:44.000
<i>I was told all you earth ponies smell</i>
<i>like rotten sardines, but you do not.</i>

23:44.041 --> 23:45.041
<i>Hmm!</i>

23:45.083 --> 23:47.958
<i>What else do unicorns say</i>
<i>about earth ponies?</i>

23:48.000 --> 23:51.833
<i>Oh, just that you're lazy and not</i>
<i>the brightest crystals in the forest.</i>

23:51.875 --> 23:54.041
<i>- Charming.</i>
<i>- No, just those three.</i>

23:54.083 --> 23:55.375
<i>So, what's the plan?</i>

23:56.375 --> 23:58.333
<i>Wait, I've got it.</i>

23:58.375 --> 24:01.000
<i>Izzy, we're going on a quest -</i>

24:01.041 --> 24:02.541
<i>to Zephyr Heights.</i>

24:02.583 --> 24:05.916
<i>- The pegasus city?</i>
<i>- Yes. We need to find out</i>

24:05.958 --> 24:08.458
<i>what happened to your magic</i>
<i>and bring it back.</i>

24:08.500 --> 24:10.708
<i>They have magic. Maybe they can help.</i>

24:10.750 --> 24:12.875
<i>But the pegasi are bad news.</i>

24:12.916 --> 24:14.750
<i>What if you're wrong about them?</i>

24:14.791 --> 24:17.291
<i>Earth ponies were wrong</i>
<i>about unicorns.</i>

24:17.333 --> 24:19.958
<i>They could welcome us</i>
<i>with open wings.</i>

24:20.000 --> 24:21.500
<i>But what if they don't?</i>

24:22.750 --> 24:24.875
<i># Up ahead, is the sky growing dark?</i>

24:24.916 --> 24:27.250
<i># Where it leads is</i>
<i>a big question mark</i>

24:27.291 --> 24:31.250
<i># And I'm scared that I'll end up</i>
<i>a pony gone missing from pegasus-ing</i>

24:31.291 --> 24:32.708
<i># But you're not alone</i>

24:32.750 --> 24:35.625
<i># You got a pony in your crew</i>

24:35.666 --> 24:37.291
<i># I do? Who?</i>

24:37.333 --> 24:39.750
<i># I'm lookin' out for you</i>

24:39.791 --> 24:41.416
<i># When you're off track</i>

24:42.666 --> 24:44.416
<i># I got your back</i>

24:44.458 --> 24:45.916
<i># You can rely on me</i>

24:45.958 --> 24:47.583
<i># I'm lookin' out for you</i>

24:47.625 --> 24:49.791
<i># Back at home</i>
<i>it was earth ponies first</i>

24:49.833 --> 24:52.083
<i># Heard it so many times</i>
<i>I could burst</i>

24:52.125 --> 24:54.416
<i># And I fought for a change</i>
<i>but it's lonely</i>

24:54.458 --> 24:56.541
<i># Cos, you know, party of uno</i>

24:56.583 --> 24:59.916
<i># Well, if you need a friendly steed</i>
