<i>(GENTLE MUSIC)</i>

35:54.625 --> 35:57.166
<i>(FRENCH ACCENT)</i>
<i>This princess smells.</i>

35:57.208 --> 35:58.875
<i>So could you.</i>

36:01.458 --> 36:03.541
<i>Parfum La Pipp.</i>

36:10.375 --> 36:12.041
<i>Something is not right.</i>

36:12.083 --> 36:15.125
<i>We haven't seen a single pony flying,</i>

36:15.166 --> 36:16.875
<i>except the royal family.</i>

36:16.916 --> 36:18.458
<i>Izzy? Are you listening?</i>

36:18.500 --> 36:22.000
<i>- (CHAIR VIBRATES)</i>
<i>- This isn't dungeony at all.</i>

36:23.041 --> 36:24.416
<i>- Uh-h-h-h...</i>
<i>- Hey!</i>

36:24.458 --> 36:28.166
<i>I'm sorry you two got thrown in here,</i>
<i>but I have to talk to you.</i>

36:28.208 --> 36:29.208
<i>Princess?</i>

36:29.250 --> 36:31.333
<i>Your Majesticness.</i>
<i>Y-Your Graceful Highness.</i>

36:31.375 --> 36:33.416
<i>Zipp. Just call me Zipp.</i>

36:33.458 --> 36:35.500
<i>OK, Zipp. I'm Sunny.</i>

36:35.541 --> 36:37.250
<i>And this is my friend.</i>

36:37.291 --> 36:39.041
<i>Izzy Moonbow.</i>

36:39.083 --> 36:43.666
<i>Sunny, Izzy, I really need to ask you</i>
<i>something important.</i>

36:43.708 --> 36:46.375
<i>- (WHISPERS) About magic.</i>
<i>- That's why we're here.</i>

36:46.416 --> 36:48.416
<i>Maybe you can tell us</i>
<i>how yours works?</i>

36:48.458 --> 36:51.166
<i>Izzy has no idea how the unicorns</i>
<i>lost theirs. So we thought maybe...</i>

36:51.208 --> 36:53.083
<i>Whoa, whoa, wait.</i>

36:53.125 --> 36:55.708
<i>Lost theirs? As in no magic?</i>

36:56.791 --> 36:58.916
<i>Well, that changes things.</i>

36:58.958 --> 37:01.750
<i>Listen, I might have</i>
<i>some information that could help,</i>

37:01.791 --> 37:04.708
<i>but first, you need to tell me</i>
<i>about this.</i>

37:04.750 --> 37:06.833
<i>My journal! Thank you, Zipp.</i>

37:06.875 --> 37:08.791
<i>I never thought I'd see it again.</i>

37:08.833 --> 37:11.833
<i>Yeah, I can be pretty sneaky</i>
<i>when I want to be.</i>

37:11.875 --> 37:13.375
<i>Nice!</i>

37:13.416 --> 37:15.250
<i>I'm only medium sneaky.</i>

37:15.291 --> 37:16.875
<i>So where did that come from?</i>

37:16.916 --> 37:19.625
<i>It was my father's. Why?</i>

37:19.666 --> 37:21.500
<i>That star...</i>

37:21.541 --> 37:24.250
<i>(FANFARE)</i>

37:28.875 --> 37:32.541
<i>Zipp, what are you doing here?</i>
<i>Mom said to stay away.</i>

37:32.583 --> 37:35.375
<i>- Right. Then why are you here?</i>
<i>- For the content.</i>

37:35.416 --> 37:37.000
<i>Princess?</i>

37:37.041 --> 37:39.916
<i>- Why isn't anypony flying?</i>
<i>- (GASPS)</i>

37:39.958 --> 37:41.041
<i>(LAUGHS)</i>

37:41.083 --> 37:43.916
<i>Everypony knows that</i>
<i>only royals can fly, of course.</i>

37:43.958 --> 37:45.541
<i>BOTH: What?</i>

37:45.583 --> 37:49.083
<i>I know, it's not fair,</i>
<i>but that's just the way it is.</i>

37:49.125 --> 37:51.666
<i>If there was some way we could</i>
<i>teach the citizens to fly,</i>

37:51.708 --> 37:53.333
<i>you know we would in a wing-beat.</i>

37:53.375 --> 37:54.708
<i>Right, Zipp?</i>

37:54.750 --> 37:56.583
<i>Yeah. In a wing-beat.</i>

37:58.875 --> 38:00.125
<i>(PHONE BUZZES)</i>

38:00.166 --> 38:01.666
<i>Oh, dress rehearsals. Gotta go.</i>

38:01.708 --> 38:02.916
<i>And so should you.</i>

38:02.958 --> 38:04.750
<i># Me-me-me!</i>

38:04.791 --> 38:07.166
<i># Red feather, yellow feather</i>
<i>Red feather, yellow feather... #</i>

38:07.208 --> 38:09.708
<i>(PIPP TRILLS)</i>

38:09.750 --> 38:11.333
<i>I have to show you something.</i>

38:13.916 --> 38:15.333
<i>(BOTH GASP)</i>

38:15.375 --> 38:16.708
<i>You coming or what?</i>

38:20.541 --> 38:22.625
<i>(GIGGLING)</i>

38:24.666 --> 38:27.208
<i>(WIND WHISTLES)</i>

38:27.250 --> 38:28.791
<i>(GRUNTS)</i>

38:28.833 --> 38:30.708
<i>(BUNNIES SQUEAK)</i>

38:34.583 --> 38:36.041
<i>(BUNNIES SQUEAK)</i>

38:37.416 --> 38:39.166
<i>Litter.</i>

38:39.208 --> 38:41.083
<i>- I mean, a clue.</i>
<i>- Oh!</i>

38:41.125 --> 38:43.541
<i>Hmm. Unicorn hair.</i>

38:46.333 --> 38:47.958
<i>Pegasi.</i>

38:50.208 --> 38:51.500
<i>Track's gone cold.</i>

38:52.791 --> 38:54.875
<i>Sunny, Sunny, Sunny, Sunny.</i>

38:54.916 --> 38:56.625
<i>You think you've escaped?</i>

38:56.666 --> 38:58.916
<i>Well, think again.</i>

38:58.958 --> 39:01.458
<i>I will not eat, I will not sleep...</i>

39:01.500 --> 39:03.166
<i>Well, maybe a quick nap and a snack</i>

39:03.208 --> 39:05.500
<i>if I can't find you</i>
<i>in the next few hours.</i>

39:05.541 --> 39:08.458
<i>But after that,</i>
<i>nothing will stop me!</i>

39:08.500 --> 39:10.000
<i>(HIGH-PITCHED CHEERING)</i>

39:12.083 --> 39:15.333
<i>Oh, thank you. Thank you.</i>
<i>No, no. You're too kind.</i>

39:15.375 --> 39:17.333
<i>- Also...</i>
<i>- Shhh!</i>

39:17.375 --> 39:19.583
<i>I'll follow you wherever you go.</i>

39:19.625 --> 39:23.083
<i>Whether harshest deserts,</i>
<i>the coldest tundras,</i>

39:23.125 --> 39:26.916
<i>no trail too dangerous,</i>
<i>no clue too small.</i>

39:26.958 --> 39:28.250
<i>(BUNNIES EXCLAIM)</i>

39:28.291 --> 39:30.541
<i>The past matters not! It's justice...</i>

39:30.583 --> 39:31.833
<i>Oh, what? What?</i>

39:31.875 --> 39:33.541
<i>(BUNNIES SQUEAK)</i>

39:37.833 --> 39:39.666
<i>Gotcha!</i>

39:43.375 --> 39:44.625
<i>Watch your step.</i>

39:44.666 --> 39:45.708
<i>Argh!</i>

39:48.541 --> 39:49.541
<i>(BOTH GASP)</i>

39:52.833 --> 39:55.166
<i>- Where are we?</i>
<i>- It's amazing, right?</i>

39:55.208 --> 39:57.333
<i>I'm pretty sure it was</i>
<i>some sort of station</i>

39:57.375 --> 40:00.833
<i>for when earth ponies and unicorns</i>
<i>used to visit Zephyr Heights.</i>

40:00.875 --> 40:03.916
<i>It's like everypony just forgot.</i>

40:08.000 --> 40:12.166
<i>This is proof. All ponykinds</i>
<i>did used to be friends!</i>

40:12.208 --> 40:13.750
<i>My dad was right.</i>

40:20.708 --> 40:24.541
<i>Must be really weird,</i>
<i>being the only pegasi that can fly.</i>

40:25.833 --> 40:29.041
<i>(SIGHS)</i>
<i>The truth is, we can't fly either.</i>

40:29.083 --> 40:30.708
<i>We've been faking it.</i>

40:30.750 --> 40:34.291
<i>Faking it? But-But how?</i>

40:34.333 --> 40:37.791
<i>You'd be surprised what some wires</i>
<i>and good lighting will do.</i>

40:37.833 --> 40:41.458
<i>But I'm just so tired</i>
<i>of living that ridiculous lie.</i>

40:41.500 --> 40:43.541
<i>That's why I come down here -</i>

40:43.583 --> 40:46.083
<i>to get away from all of that, and...</i>

40:46.125 --> 40:47.916
<i>...well, to do this.</i>

40:50.500 --> 40:51.666
<i>(WHOOSH OF AIR)</i>

40:54.750 --> 40:56.291
<i>- Wow.</i>
<i>- Whoa!</i>

40:59.666 --> 41:02.791
<i>Her sparkle is so bright right now!</i>

41:05.375 --> 41:07.875
<i>But that's not why</i>
<i>I brought you down here.</i>

41:07.916 --> 41:10.458
<i>This is what I wanted to show you.</i>

41:12.416 --> 41:14.916
<i>Oh, my stars.</i>

41:14.958 --> 41:17.416
<i>This was made a long, long time ago,</i>

41:17.458 --> 41:19.083
<i>when we still had magic.</i>

41:19.125 --> 41:20.625
<i>It's beautiful!</i>

41:22.708 --> 41:25.208
<i>- SUNNY: What is that?</i>
<i>- ZIPP: That's the pegasus crystal.</i>

41:25.250 --> 41:26.958
<i>It's part of my mom's crown.</i>

41:30.250 --> 41:33.083
<i>Hmm. Where is the unicorn crystal?</i>

41:48.750 --> 41:50.541
<i>Look.</i>

41:50.583 --> 41:52.041
<i>They fit?</i>

41:52.083 --> 41:54.458
<i>These two crystals belong together.</i>

41:54.500 --> 41:56.000
<i>United.</i>

41:56.041 --> 41:58.000
<i>So, what are you saying?</i>

41:58.041 --> 42:02.458
<i>Maybe you lost your magic</i>
<i>because the crystals were separated.</i>

42:02.500 --> 42:06.250
<i>So if we put them back together...</i>

42:06.291 --> 42:08.000
<i>...magic will return?</i>

42:08.041 --> 42:10.833
<i>And all three ponykinds</i>
<i>will get along again!</i>

42:10.875 --> 42:12.541
<i>- All right!</i>
<i>- Oh-ho-ho!</i>

42:12.583 --> 42:14.250
<i>But what about the unicorn crystal?</i>

42:14.291 --> 42:16.000
<i>Well, if you're looking for crystals.</i>

42:16.041 --> 42:18.666
<i>we've got, like, a gazillion of them</i>
<i>back in Bridlewood.</i>

42:18.708 --> 42:21.958
<i>Then that's where we'll go next.</i>
<i>After we get the pegasus crystal</i>

42:22.000 --> 42:23.291
<i>from your mom, of course.</i>

42:23.333 --> 42:25.291
<i>Ooh, that'll be tricky.</i>

42:25.333 --> 42:28.166
<i>She never takes her crown off.</i>

42:28.208 --> 42:29.666
<i>(SNORING)</i>

42:29.708 --> 42:31.833
<i># Keeping the queen clean! #</i>

42:34.458 --> 42:35.875
<i>So, what do we do?</i>

42:35.916 --> 42:38.875
<i>I got it! Pipp's performing</i>
<i>at tonight's royal celebration.</i>

42:38.916 --> 42:42.458
<i>All eyes will be on her,</i>
<i>especially my mom's.</i>

42:42.500 --> 42:44.000
<i>She'll be distracted.</i>

42:44.041 --> 42:47.875
<i>So we just need to swap</i>
<i>the real crown with a fake.</i>

42:47.916 --> 42:49.791
<i>Ooh, I can craft a decoy!</i>

42:49.833 --> 42:51.875
<i>But I will need a box of macaroni,</i>

42:51.916 --> 42:53.500
<i>a tube of glue, 14 gooey bunnies</i>

42:53.541 --> 42:54.958
<i>and three jellybeans.</i>

42:55.000 --> 42:57.833
<i>Oh, and glitter. Lots of glitter.</i>

42:59.916 --> 43:01.375
<i>ZIPP: I'll get the supplies.</i>

43:01.416 --> 43:04.500
<i>I'll pass them off to Sunny,</i>
<i>and then she will get them to you.</i>

43:06.083 --> 43:09.166
<i>Once you produce the decoy,</i>
<i>get your flanks to the palace.</i>

43:09.208 --> 43:12.041
<i>Everypony who's anypony</i>
<i>will be there,</i>

43:12.083 --> 43:13.625
<i>so security will be tight.</i>

43:13.666 --> 43:15.333
<i>(REPORTERS CLAMOUR)</i>

43:16.875 --> 43:21.083
<i>I'll distract them,</i>
<i>so you can sneak in.</i>

43:21.125 --> 43:23.375
<i>IZZY: Maximum sneaky.</i>

43:23.416 --> 43:26.416
<i>ZIPP: You'll need to be stealthy.</i>
<i>Carefully make your way</i>

43:26.458 --> 43:28.541
<i>to the Grand Hall,</i>
<i>but watch out for the guards.</i>

43:28.583 --> 43:29.875
<i>- Oh!</i>
<i>- Oh!</i>

43:31.750 --> 43:33.208
<i>(CLINK)</i>

43:35.250 --> 43:37.958
<i>ZIPP: I will open the door</i>
<i>to the back stage of the Throne Room.</i>

43:41.125 --> 43:43.625
<i>And once Pipp starts singing,</i>
<i>my mom will be so caught up,</i>

43:43.666 --> 43:46.083
<i>that swapping the crowns</i>
<i>will be easy-breezy.</i>

43:47.333 --> 43:48.750
<i>SUNNY: Easy-breezy.</i>

43:48.791 --> 43:49.958
<i>Sure.</i>

43:53.000 --> 43:55.083
<i>I hear you paid our guests a visit.</i>

43:55.125 --> 43:56.250
<i>Pipp told you?</i>

43:56.291 --> 43:58.375
<i>Oh, you know she tells me everything.</i>

43:58.416 --> 44:00.375
<i>I wish you would tell me more.</i>

44:00.416 --> 44:03.916
<i>You're going to be queen one day.</i>
<i>You'll wear this crown.</i>

44:03.958 --> 44:07.166
<i>And trust me,</i>
<i>it is heavier than it looks.</i>

44:07.208 --> 44:10.666
<i>Actually, there is something</i>
<i>I wanted to tell you.</i>

44:10.708 --> 44:12.500
<i>The unicorns don't have any magic.</i>

44:12.541 --> 44:14.583
<i>I think it's tied to</i>
<i>why we can't fly...</i>

44:14.625 --> 44:17.125
<i>Zephyrina!</i>
<i>I don't know what silly ideas</i>

44:17.166 --> 44:19.208
<i>that unicorn put into your head,</i>

44:19.250 --> 44:21.625
<i>but we have a duty</i>
<i>to protect our citizens.</i>

44:21.666 --> 44:25.041
<i>Pegasi are happy enough</i>
<i>knowing that we royals can fly.</i>

44:25.083 --> 44:26.958
<i>Why would you want</i>
<i>to disrupt things?</i>

44:27.000 --> 44:28.000
<i>Because it's a lie.</i>

44:28.041 --> 44:30.083
<i>It makes them feel safe.</i>

44:30.125 --> 44:32.125
<i>Oh, one day you'll understand.</i>

44:32.166 --> 44:33.458
<i>Your sister does.</i>

44:33.500 --> 44:36.250
<i>- Oh, and here she is now.</i>
<i>- # Me-me-me! #</i>

44:36.291 --> 44:38.625
<i>Showtime!</i>

44:38.666 --> 44:41.458
<i>We are go for launch.</i>

44:41.500 --> 44:44.666
<i>(MUSIC PLAYING)</i>

44:44.708 --> 44:47.041
<i>Remember to smile!</i>

44:47.083 --> 44:48.916
<i>Ugh.</i>

44:56.083 --> 44:59.958
<i># We got the light</i>
<i>We’re coming in stronger</i>

45:00.000 --> 45:01.750
<i># We’re in it together</i>

45:01.791 --> 45:04.458
<i># If you want it</i>
<i>It’s all inside your mind</i>

45:04.500 --> 45:08.125
<i># We got the light</i>
<i>We won’t wait any longer</i>

45:08.166 --> 45:10.333
<i># We’ll get it together</i>

45:10.375 --> 45:13.541
<i># If you want it</i>
<i>Then you can paint the sky</i>

45:13.583 --> 45:18.000
<i># Used to care what they’d say</i>
<i>Let ‘em into my brain</i>

45:18.041 --> 45:22.166
<i># But I found a new way</i>
<i>Oh-oh-oh... #</i>

45:22.208 --> 45:23.958
<i>No, you hang up.</i>

45:24.000 --> 45:25.291
<i>No...</i>

45:26.500 --> 45:27.916
<i>(GROWLS)</i>

45:27.958 --> 45:29.500
<i>Argh!</i>

45:29.541 --> 45:33.166
<i># We don’t fly like we used to</i>
<i>We take what we’ve been through</i>

45:33.208 --> 45:35.500
<i># And we can feel brand-new... #</i>

45:35.541 --> 45:36.625
<i>Aah!</i>

45:36.666 --> 45:38.583
<i>Sunny Starscout,</i>
<i>you are under arrest...</i>

45:38.625 --> 45:41.250
<i>(BARKING)</i>

45:41.291 --> 45:42.375
<i>Oh!</i>

45:42.416 --> 45:45.958
<i># I’m shining brighter</i>
<i>Ooh-ooh</i>

45:47.333 --> 45:49.000
<i># Glowing up</i>
<i>Kind of love</i>

45:49.041 --> 45:51.500
<i># Dip and slide</i>
<i>Through the cut</i>

45:51.541 --> 45:53.791
<i># Glowing up</i>
<i>Kind of love</i>

45:53.833 --> 45:55.666
<i># Dip and slide</i>
<i>Through the cut</i>

45:55.708 --> 45:57.458
<i># Glowing up</i>
<i>Kind of love</i>

45:57.500 --> 45:59.791
<i># We say high</i>
<i>You say what?</i>

45:59.833 --> 46:04.041
<i># Everywhere that I’ve been</i>
<i>Yeah, they say I’m different</i>

46:04.083 --> 46:07.541
<i># But I’m good in my skin</i>
<i>Ooh-ooh</i>

46:07.583 --> 46:10.166
<i>- (GRUNTS)</i>
<i>- # If it doesn’t feel right</i>

46:10.208 --> 46:12.083
<i># Break it in with tie-dye</i>

46:12.125 --> 46:15.083
<i># And don’t you stop till sunrise</i>

46:15.125 --> 46:16.958
<i># We don’t fly like we used to</i>

46:17.000 --> 46:19.083
<i># We take what we’ve been through</i>

46:19.125 --> 46:22.208
<i># And we can feel brand-new</i>
<i>Ooh-ooh... #</i>

46:23.750 --> 46:25.958
<i>Oh! It's the prisoners! (WAILS)</i>

46:26.000 --> 46:27.750
<i>- Shh!</i>
<i>- Quiet!</i>

46:27.791 --> 46:31.666
<i># I'm shining brighter</i>
<i>Ooh-ooh-ooh</i>

46:31.708 --> 46:35.750
<i># We got the light</i>
<i>We’re coming in stronger</i>

46:35.791 --> 46:37.583
<i># We’re in it together... #</i>

46:37.625 --> 46:38.916
<i>It's OK - don't be scared.</i>

46:38.958 --> 46:40.625
<i>I'm not going to fry your brain, OK?</i>

46:40.666 --> 46:42.416
<i>Argh!</i>

46:42.458 --> 46:44.791
<i>What the...?</i>

46:44.833 --> 46:47.500
<i>(MUSIC CONTINUES)</i>

46:47.541 --> 46:48.875
<i>Uh...</i>

46:48.916 --> 46:51.208
<i># Throwing up</i>
<i>Find a glove</i>

46:51.250 --> 46:53.208
<i># Fly around, bup-bup-bup</i>

46:53.250 --> 46:54.958
<i># Doing stuff that I love</i>

46:55.000 --> 46:57.500
<i># You're like, why?</i>
<i>I'm like what? #</i>

46:57.541 --> 46:59.125
<i>What is happening?</i>

46:59.166 --> 47:01.208
<i># Crisp and dry</i>
<i>Eat some mud</i>

47:01.250 --> 47:03.583
<i># Glowing up</i>
<i>Lovey dove... #</i>

47:04.666 --> 47:06.041
<i>(SCREAMS)</i>

47:06.083 --> 47:07.333
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

47:09.791 --> 47:11.375
<i>Aaah!</i>

47:11.416 --> 47:13.000
<i>- I got it!</i>
<i>- Yes!</i>

47:13.041 --> 47:14.041
<i>Let's go!</i>

47:14.083 --> 47:15.750
<i>Freeze.</i>

47:15.791 --> 47:17.833
<i>PEGASUS FAN: It's the prisoners!</i>

47:19.208 --> 47:20.541
<i>Another earth pony!</i>

47:26.458 --> 47:27.791
<i>(CROWD GASPS)</i>

47:27.833 --> 47:30.000
<i>- She's a fake!</i>
<i>- Fake!</i>

47:30.041 --> 47:32.125
<i>The royals can't fly either?!</i>

47:33.333 --> 47:35.500
<i>- Fake!</i>
<i>- Zipp?</i>

47:35.541 --> 47:37.208
<i>Zipp! Hurry!</i>

47:37.250 --> 47:39.416
<i>FAN: They can't fly?!</i>

47:39.458 --> 47:41.458
<i>She's faking it!</i>

47:41.500 --> 47:43.250
<i>She's a fake!</i>

47:43.291 --> 47:45.708
<i>(SIRENS)</i>

47:45.750 --> 47:47.041
<i>Quick! This way.</i>

47:50.583 --> 47:52.875
<i>- (THUMP)</i>
<i>- OK, I think we lost them.</i>

47:52.916 --> 47:54.208
<i>(SQUEAKING)</i>

47:54.250 --> 47:56.083
<i>Hitch, what are you even doing here?</i>

47:56.125 --> 47:58.500
<i>Arresting you. And saving you.</i>

47:58.541 --> 48:00.541
<i>So, you know, a little bit of both,</i>
<i>actually.</i>

48:00.583 --> 48:01.625
<i>You're welcome.</i>

48:01.666 --> 48:04.666
<i>Oh, gee, thanks.</i>
<i>But we don't need any saving. OK?</i>

48:04.708 --> 48:06.458
<i>And you are?</i>

48:06.500 --> 48:07.666
<i>Her mom is the Queen!</i>

48:07.708 --> 48:10.583
<i>Wait a minute.</i>
<i>So that means you're a princess?</i>

48:10.625 --> 48:13.166
<i>Huh, look at that. The sheriff</i>
<i>just became a detective.</i>

48:13.208 --> 48:14.583
<i>- What?</i>
<i>- (TV JINGLE)</i>

48:14.625 --> 48:17.208
<i>Breaking story.</i>
<i>Zephyr Heights is in turmoil tonight</i>

48:17.250 --> 48:20.500
<i>after the shocking revelation</i>
<i>that the royals cannot fly.</i>

48:20.541 --> 48:22.166
<i>Pipp used to be my favourite.</i>

48:22.208 --> 48:25.000
<i>If we can't trust our own royalty,</i>
<i>who can we trust?</i>

48:25.041 --> 48:27.041
<i>I blame the unicorns</i>
<i>and the earth ponies.</i>

48:27.083 --> 48:28.500
<i>They ruin everything!</i>

48:28.541 --> 48:31.291
<i>This just in. Queen Haven has been</i>
<i>arrested for being a phony pony</i>

48:31.333 --> 48:32.833
<i>- full of baloney.</i>
<i>- (GASPS)</i>

48:32.875 --> 48:35.000
<i>No comment, and no photos!</i>

48:35.041 --> 48:36.666
<i>OK, one photo.</i>

48:36.708 --> 48:38.416
<i>Anypony care to explain?</i>

48:38.458 --> 48:40.333
<i>We had to get the crystal!</i>

48:40.375 --> 48:41.375
<i>Look.</i>

48:41.416 --> 48:43.125
<i>Oh, no, no, no, no, no.</i>

48:43.166 --> 48:45.208
<i>- It's not here!</i>
<i>- Seriously?</i>

48:45.250 --> 48:48.000
<i>On the bright side,</i>
<i>we had so much fun losing it.</i>

48:48.041 --> 48:49.166
<i>We have to go back.</i>

48:49.208 --> 48:50.541
<i>But it could be anywhere!</i>

48:50.583 --> 48:52.041
<i>(CLATTER)</i>

48:55.000 --> 48:58.541
<i>Somepony seriously needs to explain</i>
<i>why this thing was so important</i>

48:58.583 --> 49:00.666
<i>that you had to ruin</i>
<i>my whole show over it.</i>

49:00.708 --> 49:02.000
<i>Trust me, it was.</i>

49:02.041 --> 49:05.583
<i>You left me hanging there</i>
<i>in the spotlight.</i>

49:05.625 --> 49:07.916
<i>Now everypony knows we can't fly.</i>

49:07.958 --> 49:09.458
<i>(PHONE ALERT)</i>

49:09.500 --> 49:12.416
<i>A warrant is out for the arrest</i>
<i>of the princesses.</i>

49:12.458 --> 49:14.916
<i>Pipp! Zipp! Save yourselves.</i>

49:14.958 --> 49:17.375
<i>What?! This isn't happening.</i>

49:17.416 --> 49:19.083
<i>- This is so not happening!</i>
<i>- Pipp!</i>

49:19.125 --> 49:22.750
<i>Forget about all that. We think</i>
<i>we can bring back magic,</i>

49:22.791 --> 49:24.250
<i>but we need that crystal.</i>

49:24.291 --> 49:25.750
<i>Have you lost your mind?</i>

49:25.791 --> 49:27.958
<i>Please. This might be</i>
<i>our only chance.</i>

49:29.291 --> 49:30.708
<i>Oh, fine!</i>

49:30.750 --> 49:32.083
<i>I know a way out.</i>

49:32.125 --> 49:33.541
<i>Come on.</i>

49:33.583 --> 49:35.791
<i>What? Wait! You can't just...</i>

49:35.833 --> 49:37.458
<i>But I'm a sheriff!</i>

49:37.500 --> 49:38.625
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

49:53.000 --> 49:55.458
<i>- Hey!</i>
<i>- (YELLING)</i>

50:03.208 --> 50:07.791
<i>(RASPY BREATHING)</i>

50:12.750 --> 50:14.083
<i>(SLURPS)</i>

50:14.125 --> 50:15.958
<i>Why aren't you finished yet?</i>

50:16.000 --> 50:19.041
<i>We're working as fast as we can,</i>
<i>but we've run out of rivets.</i>

50:19.083 --> 50:21.666
<i>Riveting story. (LAUGHS)</i>

50:23.541 --> 50:25.708
<i>(SIGHS) Just make it work, OK?</i>

50:25.750 --> 50:26.833
<i>(YELLS)</i>

50:26.875 --> 50:29.875
<i>Sugar cube,</i>
<i>I know your little top-secret project</i>

50:29.916 --> 50:32.041
<i>is important and all,</i>

50:32.083 --> 50:33.500
<i>but when do you think my workers</i>

50:33.541 --> 50:35.666
<i>can get back to making</i>
<i>Canterlogic products?</i>

50:35.708 --> 50:36.708
<i>(YELLING)</i>

50:37.708 --> 50:38.916
<i>(THUMP)</i>

50:38.958 --> 50:40.375
<i>Back to work, Glitter Cupcake!</i>

50:40.416 --> 50:42.916
<i>It is my factory, after all, dear.</i>

50:42.958 --> 50:44.541
<i>It's my town, Mommy.</i>

50:44.583 --> 50:48.208
<i>Your son's now Emperor</i>
<i>of Maretime Bay.</i>

50:48.250 --> 50:49.791
<i>Emperor?!</i>

50:49.833 --> 50:51.958
<i>But yesterday</i>
<i>you were only the sheriff.</i>

50:52.000 --> 50:54.875
<i>Well, see how fast</i>
<i>I'm climbing the ranks?</i>

50:54.916 --> 50:58.708
<i>This defence factory</i>
<i>is going on offence,</i>

50:58.750 --> 51:03.208
<i>and it's all thanks to your love</i>
<i>and encouragement.</i>

51:03.250 --> 51:05.250
<i>Break's over, Bubblegum McGinty!</i>

51:05.291 --> 51:06.500
<i>Oh, dear.</i>

51:06.541 --> 51:08.708
<i>Somepony's getting a big head.</i>

51:12.416 --> 51:14.541
<i>That's the tree from the map!</i>

51:14.583 --> 51:16.708
<i>That means...it's this way.</i>

51:18.541 --> 51:19.791
<i>What am I even doing here,</i>

51:19.833 --> 51:21.375
<i>hoofing it across Daisy Fields,</i>

51:21.416 --> 51:23.958
<i>looking for a magical crystal</i>
<i>that doesn't even exist!</i>

51:24.000 --> 51:26.250
<i>It was supposed to be</i>
<i>my best show ever.</i>

51:26.291 --> 51:27.750
<i>Now it's all over.</i>

51:27.791 --> 51:29.208
<i>I'm a criminal,</i>

51:29.250 --> 51:31.958
<i>- and it's all because of them.</i>
<i>- Them.</i>

51:32.000 --> 51:33.708
<i>And that is so not cool.</i>

51:33.750 --> 51:35.666
<i>No, it is not.</i>

51:35.708 --> 51:37.250
<i>Did I just agree with a pegasus?</i>

51:37.291 --> 51:41.666
<i>Hey, are you sure she even knows</i>
<i>where to find this other crystal?</i>

51:41.708 --> 51:43.125
<i>Don't you trust me at all?</i>

51:43.166 --> 51:44.208
<i>I don't know.</i>

51:44.250 --> 51:46.583
<i>You are the one that just got Mom</i>
<i>thrown in jail.</i>

51:46.625 --> 51:50.291
<i>Look, once we get our magic back,</i>
<i>the whole kingdom will be so excited,</i>

51:50.333 --> 51:52.875
<i>they won't even remember</i>
<i>what happened back there.</i>

51:52.916 --> 51:54.458
<i>You'll be a hero, Pipp.</i>

51:56.000 --> 51:57.333
<i>Let's get one thing straight.</i>

51:57.375 --> 51:59.083
<i>We're almost to the river, everypony!</i>

51:59.125 --> 52:00.833
<i>After this whole escapade</i>
<i>is over with,</i>

52:00.875 --> 52:03.250
<i>you are going to march back home</i>
<i>to Maretime Bay with me.</i>

52:03.291 --> 52:05.208
<i>- Is that clear?</i>
<i>- Crystal.</i>

52:05.250 --> 52:08.166
<i>Great. Because this badge</i>
<i>means that I'm the sher...</i>

52:08.208 --> 52:09.208
<i>Argh!</i>

52:09.250 --> 52:12.208
<i>No, no, no, no!</i>
<i>Where's my badge? Hey!</i>

52:12.250 --> 52:13.333
<i>- You.</i>
<i>- Hmm?</i>

52:13.375 --> 52:15.875
<i>I know unicorns like shiny things.</i>

52:15.916 --> 52:18.500
<i>Oh, you know, I think I did see</i>
<i>a shiny badgey thing on the ground</i>

52:18.541 --> 52:20.958
<i>- a few hours ago.</i>
<i>- What? Hours?!</i>

52:21.000 --> 52:24.083
<i>Well, maybe it's for the best.</i>
<i>Between you and me, buddy,</i>

52:24.125 --> 52:27.583
<i>that badge was creating</i>
<i>an unhealthy power dynamic.</i>

52:27.625 --> 52:29.583
<i>(SINGS)</i>

52:34.625 --> 52:35.958
<i>(GASPS)</i>

52:38.625 --> 52:40.291
<i>Where are we going to do?</i>

52:40.333 --> 52:41.708
<i>Any ideas, Zipp?</i>

52:41.750 --> 52:43.916
<i>You know what would be great</i>
<i>right now? Let me think.</i>

52:43.958 --> 52:45.666
<i>Maybe something like</i>
<i>the ability to fly?</i>

52:45.708 --> 52:47.166
<i>You know what would be even better?</i>

52:47.208 --> 52:49.083
<i>Not being stuck in the middle</i>
<i>of nowhere...</i>

52:49.125 --> 52:51.250
<i>Oh, well! That's the end of that.</i>
<i>Time to go home.</i>

52:51.291 --> 52:54.041
<i>I wish I could say it was nice</i>
<i>meeting all of you, but it wasn't.</i>

52:54.083 --> 52:55.958
<i>- Come on, Sunny.</i>
<i>- I don't think so.</i>

52:56.000 --> 52:57.208
<i>Everypony stop.</i>

52:58.250 --> 53:01.375
<i>We're gonna get to the other side,</i>
<i>find the crystal,</i>

53:01.416 --> 53:03.083
<i>and bring back magic.</i>

53:03.125 --> 53:05.500
<i>And once we do, you'll get to fly,</i>

53:05.541 --> 53:08.458
<i>you'll get your fans back,</i>
<i>and you'll have me in custody.</i>

53:08.500 --> 53:09.875
<i>Everypony happy now?</i>

53:09.916 --> 53:11.333
<i>(CRASH)</i>

53:11.375 --> 53:12.875
<i>Ta-da!</i>

53:15.375 --> 53:17.416
<i>- All right.</i>
<i>- Ah, great.</i>

53:17.458 --> 53:18.791
<i>Come on, everypony.</i>

53:23.833 --> 53:25.000
<i>(YELLING)</i>

53:27.250 --> 53:29.833
<i>Oh, yeah! Nailed it!</i>

53:29.875 --> 53:31.791
<i>Come on, stupid stick.</i>

53:31.833 --> 53:33.375
<i>You need some backup, Sheriff?</i>

53:33.416 --> 53:35.875
<i>No, thank you. I've got it.</i>

53:35.916 --> 53:37.916
<i>Come on. If I only had a match.</i>

53:37.958 --> 53:39.791
<i>Ah! Oh.</i>

53:39.833 --> 53:42.333
<i>- Oh, well, that was sad to watch.</i>
<i>- Come on, don't be a hero, dude.</i>

53:42.375 --> 53:44.208
<i>Come get warm.</i>

53:44.250 --> 53:46.208
<i>Are you sure about all this?</i>

53:46.250 --> 53:48.250
<i>Because if we just go back</i>
<i>to Maretime Bay...</i>

53:48.291 --> 53:49.833
<i>What have we got to lose?</i>

53:49.875 --> 53:53.208
<i>By giving magic back to our enemies?</i>
<i>Uh, let me think.</i>

53:53.250 --> 53:55.583
<i>- I know - a lot!</i>
<i>- Come on.</i>

53:55.625 --> 53:57.666
<i>Do they look like enemies to you?</i>

53:57.708 --> 53:59.541
<i>My sparkle is aquamarine?</i>

53:59.583 --> 54:01.291
<i>That's like</i>
<i>my sixth-favourite colour!</i>

54:01.333 --> 54:02.875
<i>(SIGHS) I don't know.</i>

54:02.916 --> 54:06.166
<i>Maybe I should just go back</i>
<i>to Maretime Bay, where I'm needed.</i>

54:06.208 --> 54:07.625
<i>If that's what you want.</i>

54:07.666 --> 54:11.666
<i>But you should know</i>
<i>I'm actually glad you're here, Hitch.</i>

54:11.708 --> 54:13.333
<i>We all are.</i>

54:19.166 --> 54:20.416
<i>(SNORTS)</i>

54:21.708 --> 54:23.625
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

54:23.666 --> 54:26.333
<i>So, I think we should set off</i>
<i>at first light.</i>

54:26.375 --> 54:28.125
<i>Last stop, Bridlewood.</i>

54:30.958 --> 54:32.500
<i>What's wrong, Izzy?</i>

54:32.541 --> 54:35.500
<i>It's just that being with you ponies</i>

54:35.541 --> 54:38.666
<i>has been the best thing</i>
<i>that's ever happened to me.</i>

54:38.708 --> 54:42.750
<i>I guess I just don't want</i>
<i>our adventure to end.</i>

54:42.791 --> 54:45.541
<i>But, Izzy, you'll get your magic.</i>

54:47.958 --> 54:50.125
<i>Can I ask you a question?</i>

54:50.166 --> 54:52.416
<i>Why did you come to Maretime Bay?</i>

54:52.458 --> 54:55.208
<i>I always wanted to visit.</i>
<i>When I was a filly,</i>

54:55.250 --> 54:58.375
<i>I found this pretty lantern.</i>
<i>It had a message inside.</i>

54:58.416 --> 55:01.916
<i>It said I had friends</i>
<i>in Maretime Bay.</i>

55:06.666 --> 55:08.833
<i>It... It was you!</i>

55:10.000 --> 55:12.041
<i>I made it with my dad.</i>

55:13.250 --> 55:15.416
<i>We always promised each other</i>

55:15.458 --> 55:17.750
<i>that someday we would prove</i>

55:17.791 --> 55:21.083
<i>that all ponies</i>
<i>were meant to be friends.</i>

55:21.125 --> 55:24.875
<i>We'll do our part. Hoof to heart.</i>

55:33.000 --> 55:34.250
<i>Hey, um...</i>

55:36.000 --> 55:37.791
<i>I want to do my part.</i>

55:41.208 --> 55:43.083
<i>What have we got to lose, right?</i>

55:43.125 --> 55:45.333
<i>- Whoo!</i>
<i>- All right!</i>

55:45.375 --> 55:50.375
<i>I have to admit, a unicorn forest</i>
<i>does sound kind of magical.</i>

55:52.666 --> 55:54.375
<i>Or not.</i>

55:56.375 --> 55:58.958
<i>IZZY: Come on!</i>
<i>My house isn't far from here!</i>

55:59.000 --> 56:00.375
<i>(SINGS TO HERSELF)</i>

56:02.666 --> 56:04.750
<i>(IZZY CONTINUES SINGING)</i>

56:11.916 --> 56:13.958
<i>Well, here we are, guys.</i>

56:14.000 --> 56:15.750
<i>La Villa Izzy.</i>

56:16.833 --> 56:18.208
<i>ALL: Wow!</i>

56:22.875 --> 56:24.791
<i>(PLAYS TUNE)</i>

56:26.541 --> 56:28.208
<i>- Did you make all of this?</i>
<i>- Yeah!</i>

56:28.250 --> 56:31.083
<i>Unicycling. Isn't it funky?</i>

56:31.125 --> 56:33.500
<i>It is gorgeous!</i>

56:33.541 --> 56:35.958
<i>- I also make friendship bracelets.</i>
<i>- Oh, cool.</i>

56:36.000 --> 56:38.166
<i>Wait, wait, watch this!</i>
<i>Hold everything!</i>

56:38.208 --> 56:41.041
<i>Ha! I've never gotten to use it</i>
<i>with actual friends!</i>

56:42.833 --> 56:44.833
<i>- Ta-da!</i>
<i>- Oh!</i>

56:44.875 --> 56:47.375
<i>I so wish I had live-streamed that.</i>

56:47.416 --> 56:49.041
<i>We don't have time for that</i>
<i>right now.</i>

56:49.083 --> 56:51.333
<i>If we're going to get</i>
<i>the information we need</i>

56:51.375 --> 56:54.250
<i>on the unicorn crystal,</i>
<i>we can't stick out like sore hooves.</i>

56:54.291 --> 56:56.708
<i>We need to look like unicorns.</i>

56:56.750 --> 56:59.833
<i>Yay! Makeovers!</i>
<i>I love makeovers.</i>

56:59.875 --> 57:02.833
<i>No... No, this is not...</i>
<i>this is not what I signed up for. No.</i>

57:02.875 --> 57:04.625
<i>So, Izzy, can you do it?</i>

57:04.666 --> 57:06.291
<i>A glow-up?</i>

57:06.333 --> 57:09.833
<i>Honey, you came to the right cottage.</i>

57:15.500 --> 57:18.666
<i># I thought earth ponies were</i>
<i>the pony ladder’s bottom rung</i>

57:18.708 --> 57:21.416
<i># I heard that pegasi were brutes</i>
<i>you’d hate to be among</i>

57:21.458 --> 57:22.875
<i># You smell like fishes</i>
<i>You’re vicious</i>

57:22.916 --> 57:24.083
<i># I bet you eat your young!</i>

57:24.125 --> 57:26.666
<i># Meet any one of you</i>
<i>The thing to do is run away</i>

57:26.708 --> 57:30.333
<i># But although I know we’re all</i>
<i>a bunch of different breeds</i>

57:30.375 --> 57:33.250
<i># Take away our wings and horns</i>
<i>and we’re just frightened steeds</i>

57:33.291 --> 57:37.208
<i># So let’s put aside our differences</i>
<i>cos what we need’s a win</i>

57:37.250 --> 57:38.625
<i># Oh-oh-oh</i>

57:38.666 --> 57:41.375
<i># Come on, rip out all the pages</i>
<i>of your history books.</i>

57:41.416 --> 57:44.208
<i># Just because we’re undercover</i>
<i>doesn’t mean we’re crooks</i>

57:44.250 --> 57:48.541
<i># When we walk you through the crowd</i>
<i>and give your brand-new looks a spin</i>

57:48.583 --> 57:50.541
<i># You’re gonna fit right in! #</i>

57:50.583 --> 57:51.666
<i>This is a new low.</i>

57:51.708 --> 57:53.208
<i># You're gonna fit right in... #</i>

57:53.250 --> 57:54.625
<i>It's never gonna work!</i>

57:56.041 --> 57:58.875
<i># They taught us unicorns</i>
<i>were super-scary maniacs</i>

57:58.916 --> 58:01.708
<i># With horns like razors and tongues</i>
<i>like Tasers and teeth like tacks</i>

58:01.750 --> 58:04.458
<i># They take your hooves and then</i>
<i>they grind them into midnight snacks</i>

58:04.500 --> 58:07.416
<i># The basic gist of it</i>
<i>is unicorns are not OK</i>

58:07.458 --> 58:10.666
<i># Look, I know we’re risking</i>
<i>everything for this endeavour</i>

58:10.708 --> 58:13.583
<i># But look at us - we’re brave</i>
<i>and strong and weird and clever</i>

58:13.625 --> 58:18.000
<i># We’re running out of options</i>
<i>and we’re desperate to begin</i>

58:18.041 --> 58:19.625
<i># You’re gonna fit right in! #</i>

58:19.666 --> 58:21.000
<i>If you say so!</i>

58:21.041 --> 58:22.250
<i># You’re gonna fit right in! #</i>

58:22.291 --> 58:24.666
<i>I know you will -</i>
<i>now watch and learn.</i>

58:24.708 --> 58:26.833
<i># This is how a unicorn walks</i>

58:26.875 --> 58:27.916
<i># Walks</i>

58:27.958 --> 58:29.666
<i># This is how a unicorn talks</i>

58:29.708 --> 58:30.750
<i># Talks</i>

58:30.791 --> 58:32.291
<i># This is how a unicorn hoops</i>

58:32.333 --> 58:33.333
<i># Hoops</i>

58:33.375 --> 58:35.041
<i>- # This is how a unicorn... #</i>
<i>- Oops!</i>

58:35.083 --> 58:36.125
<i>Stop!</i>

58:36.166 --> 58:38.166
<i># This is how a unicorn struts</i>

58:38.208 --> 58:41.333
<i># Watch us shake our unicorn butts</i>

58:41.375 --> 58:44.208
<i>- # Now you're in the unicorn know...</i>
<i>- # Whoa</i>

58:44.250 --> 58:47.000
<i># Soon you'll make a unicorn pro! Oh</i>

58:47.041 --> 58:49.708
<i># A unicorn horn</i>
<i>makes a unicorn stride</i>

58:49.750 --> 58:52.583
<i># It's the more-head on your forehead</i>
<i>It's the source of your pride</i>

58:52.625 --> 58:55.250
<i># Every unicorn who's born</i>
<i>has worn a horn that's unique</i>

58:55.291 --> 58:57.875
<i># So we'll whip them up as we speak</i>
<i>You'll be looking très magnifique</i>

58:57.916 --> 59:00.291
<i># And with those rocks in our pockets</i>
<i>We'll reap the reward</i>

59:00.333 --> 59:02.208
<i># And folks'll be floored</i>
<i>We'll strike a new chord</i>

59:02.250 --> 59:03.666
<i># Our magic restored!</i>

59:03.708 --> 59:06.041
<i># Lately, all Equestria</i>
<i>has lost its heart</i>

59:06.083 --> 59:08.708
<i># But if we can help to find it</i>
<i>we should play our part</i>

59:08.750 --> 59:10.750
<i># If we fail, we’ll go to prison</i>

59:10.791 --> 59:13.625
<i># But if not, we’ll start to grin</i>

59:13.666 --> 59:16.083
<i># So let’s begin!</i>

59:16.125 --> 59:17.916
<i># We're gonna fit right in!</i>

59:17.958 --> 59:20.041
<i># This is how a unicorn walks!</i>

59:20.083 --> 59:23.083
<i># This is how a unicorn talks!</i>

59:23.125 --> 59:25.916
<i># Now you're looking unicorn strong</i>

59:25.958 --> 59:28.583
<i>- # This is how a unicorn</i>
<i>- # Ends this song. #</i>

59:34.791 --> 59:36.000
<i>(GIGGLES)</i>

59:36.041 --> 59:38.333
<i>Ta-da! Crystal!</i>

59:38.375 --> 59:40.875
<i>Crystal! Crystal!</i>

59:40.916 --> 59:41.958
<i>Crystal!</i>

59:42.000 --> 59:44.958
<i>She does know we're just looking</i>
<i>for the one, right?</i>

59:45.000 --> 59:46.416
<i>Crystal!</i>

59:46.458 --> 59:49.541
<i>Crystal! Crystals!</i>

59:51.000 --> 59:52.416
<i>(GIGGLES)</i>

59:59.291 --> 1:00:00.958
<i>Ow.</i>

1:00:01.000 --> 1:00:02.208
<i>Ow.</i>

1:00:04.583 --> 1:00:06.083
<i>- Hey.</i>
<i>- Hey.</i>

1:00:09.833 --> 1:00:11.958
<i>Well, this is...cheerful.</i>

1:00:12.000 --> 1:00:15.333
<i>These other unicorns</i>
<i>seem so different than you.</i>

1:00:15.375 --> 1:00:17.041
<i>Yeah, I get that a lot.</i>

1:00:17.083 --> 1:00:20.458
<i>My sparkle is a bit too sparkly</i>
<i>for Bridlewood.</i>

1:00:20.500 --> 1:00:22.958
<i>How can we tell</i>
<i>which ones are magic?</i>

1:00:23.000 --> 1:00:24.166
<i>Ooh!</i>

1:00:24.208 --> 1:00:26.375
<i>- You said a bad word!</i>
<i>- Huh?</i>

1:00:26.416 --> 1:00:28.375
<i>Hurry, before we get jinxed!</i>

1:00:28.416 --> 1:00:30.416
<i>ALL: Ah!</i>

1:00:30.458 --> 1:00:32.083
<i>(ALL BLOW AIR)</i>

1:00:32.125 --> 1:00:34.833
<i># Bing-bong-bing!</i>
<i>Bing-bong, bing-bong!</i>

1:00:34.875 --> 1:00:36.833
<i># Bing-bong, bing-bong! #</i>

1:00:36.875 --> 1:00:38.416
<i>O...K.</i>

1:00:38.458 --> 1:00:40.500
<i>I'm going to need some context.</i>

1:00:40.541 --> 1:00:42.750
<i>Unicorns are very superstitious.</i>

1:00:42.791 --> 1:00:44.833
<i>If a pony ever says</i>
<i>a forbidden word,</i>

1:00:44.875 --> 1:00:48.083
<i>we have to do a ritual</i>
<i>to ward off the jinxies.</i>

1:00:48.125 --> 1:00:50.291
<i>- Jinxies?</i>
<i>- Bad luck.</i>

1:00:50.333 --> 1:00:51.541
<i>Forbidden words?</i>

1:00:51.583 --> 1:00:54.083
<i>Magic, wing, feather...</i>

1:00:54.125 --> 1:00:55.291
<i>Oh, and mayonnaise.</i>

1:00:55.333 --> 1:00:58.375
<i>- What's wrong with may...?</i>
<i>- Ah-da-da-da-da!</i>

1:00:58.416 --> 1:01:00.958
<i>(CUCKOO CALLS)</i>

1:01:02.083 --> 1:01:03.583
<i>- (GASPS)</i>
<i>- Come on!</i>

1:01:03.625 --> 1:01:05.041
<i>There's something I want to show you.</i>

1:01:08.791 --> 1:01:10.166
<i>The Crystal Tearoom?</i>

1:01:10.208 --> 1:01:13.083
<i>There's a pony inside</i>
<i>who collects crystals.</i>

1:01:13.125 --> 1:01:14.375
<i>Maybe he could help us.</i>

1:01:14.416 --> 1:01:16.041
<i>That's great, Izzy!</i>

1:01:16.083 --> 1:01:18.458
<i>- Oh, and, Hitch...</i>
<i>- I know, I know.</i>

1:01:18.500 --> 1:01:19.875
<i>No forbidden words.</i>

1:01:23.833 --> 1:01:28.083
<i>Earth pony jinx.</i>
<i>Something stinks.</i>

1:01:28.125 --> 1:01:29.666
<i>Pegasus neighs...</i>

1:01:29.708 --> 1:01:33.583
<i>That's the pony I was talking about.</i>

1:01:33.625 --> 1:01:37.583
<i>So word in the forest is</i>
<i>you collect crystals.</i>

1:01:38.666 --> 1:01:40.333
<i>Yes, I do.</i>

1:01:40.375 --> 1:01:42.083
<i>Well, I mean, I did.</i>

1:01:42.125 --> 1:01:46.041
<i>I lost them all in a limbo contest</i>
<i>with Alphabittle.</i>

1:01:46.083 --> 1:01:47.375
<i>Oh, no.</i>

1:01:47.416 --> 1:01:49.916
<i>- Who's Alphabittle?</i>
<i>- (BELL CLANGS)</i>

1:01:49.958 --> 1:01:52.625
<i>Time's up! Pass it over, Jasper.</i>

1:01:53.791 --> 1:01:55.375
<i>Ohhh.</i>

1:01:58.583 --> 1:02:00.666
<i>Guess that makes me the winner -</i>
<i>again.</i>

1:02:00.708 --> 1:02:01.791
<i>Pay up.</i>

1:02:01.833 --> 1:02:03.958
<i>Oh, fine.</i>

1:02:05.250 --> 1:02:07.625
<i>You could always try</i>
<i>winning it back!</i>

1:02:09.583 --> 1:02:11.250
<i>All right, suit yourself.</i>

1:02:15.416 --> 1:02:16.583
<i>There it is!</i>

1:02:16.625 --> 1:02:20.458
<i>I've got an idea. Maybe I can</i>
<i>beat Alphabittle at his own game.</i>

1:02:20.500 --> 1:02:22.791
<i>Wait! Alphabittle can smell fear.</i>

1:02:22.833 --> 1:02:24.000
<i>Got it.</i>

1:02:24.041 --> 1:02:26.375
<i>OK, be cool.</i>

1:02:28.125 --> 1:02:29.208
<i>Oh...</i>

1:02:32.083 --> 1:02:33.208
<i>Tea.</i>

1:02:33.250 --> 1:02:34.791
<i>(CRITTER SQUEAKS)</i>

1:02:38.625 --> 1:02:39.875
<i>Hold the milk.</i>

1:02:39.916 --> 1:02:42.666
<i>Quite the game player, I see.</i>

1:02:42.708 --> 1:02:44.125
<i>It passes the time.</i>

1:02:44.166 --> 1:02:46.583
<i>Why. Do you play?</i>

1:02:46.625 --> 1:02:47.833
<i>I don't play.</i>

1:02:47.875 --> 1:02:48.958
<i>I win.</i>

1:02:49.000 --> 1:02:50.416
<i>Is that so?</i>

1:02:50.458 --> 1:02:51.958
<i>Yeah, it is.</i>

1:02:52.000 --> 1:02:54.041
<i>And I challenge you for that.</i>

1:02:56.291 --> 1:02:57.791
<i>You think you can beat me?</i>

1:02:57.833 --> 1:02:59.666
<i>Only one way to find out.</i>

1:02:59.708 --> 1:03:01.875
<i>Big talk for a little pony.</i>

1:03:01.916 --> 1:03:04.500
<i>I think you'll find</i>
<i>I'm average height.</i>

1:03:05.916 --> 1:03:07.791
<i>Tick-tock. What do you say?</i>

1:03:07.833 --> 1:03:10.916
<i>Whatever you're betting,</i>
<i>it better be special.</i>

1:03:12.333 --> 1:03:14.125
<i>Special enough for you?</i>

1:03:14.166 --> 1:03:15.166
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

1:03:16.541 --> 1:03:18.750
<i>(LAUGHS NERVOUSLY)</i>

1:03:18.791 --> 1:03:20.458
<i>Um...what are you doing?</i>

1:03:20.500 --> 1:03:23.750
<i>Don't worry! I could solve</i>
<i>that cube puzzle in my sleep.</i>

1:03:23.791 --> 1:03:26.083
<i>But if he wins,</i>
<i>we'll lose both crystals!</i>

1:03:26.125 --> 1:03:28.000
<i>- We won't. Trust me.</i>
<i>- Izzy.</i>

1:03:28.041 --> 1:03:30.500
<i>If your friend is finished stalling,</i>
<i>do we have a deal?</i>

1:03:30.541 --> 1:03:31.958
<i>Deal.</i>

1:03:32.000 --> 1:03:33.791
<i>Now give me that cube.</i>

1:03:33.833 --> 1:03:35.500
<i>No, no, no, no.</i>

1:03:35.541 --> 1:03:39.958
<i>A special prize</i>
<i>calls for a special competition.</i>

1:03:40.000 --> 1:03:44.250
<i>Bring forth the Ultimate Challenge!</i>

1:03:44.291 --> 1:03:45.500
<i>The ultimate what, now?</i>

1:03:50.625 --> 1:03:52.541
<i>A dancing game. Seriously?</i>

1:03:52.583 --> 1:03:56.083
<i>Both ponies agree -</i>
<i>best out of three.</i>

1:03:56.125 --> 1:03:59.375
<i>Let's make this more interesting.</i>

1:03:59.416 --> 1:04:02.500
<i>You only need to win one</i>
<i>out of three.</i>

1:04:02.541 --> 1:04:05.333
<i>(MUSIC STARTS)</i>

1:04:16.750 --> 1:04:18.875
<i>(DING!)</i>

1:04:18.916 --> 1:04:21.291
<i>Yeah! That's how you do it!</i>

1:04:21.333 --> 1:04:22.625
<i>Yay.</i>

1:04:22.666 --> 1:04:25.625
<i>It's OK. You're just warming up.</i>

1:04:25.666 --> 1:04:28.375
<i>ANNOUNCER: What can you do?</i>
<i>Round two.</i>

1:04:28.416 --> 1:04:29.875
<i>I'll make this quick.</i>

1:04:29.916 --> 1:04:30.958
<i>Focus.</i>

1:04:31.000 --> 1:04:33.083
<i>(MUSIC STARTS)</i>

1:04:38.416 --> 1:04:39.750
<i>(DING-DING-DING!)</i>

1:04:39.791 --> 1:04:41.083
<i>Yeah!</i>

1:04:41.125 --> 1:04:44.125
<i>Critters! Get my crystal polish</i>
<i>ready, would you?</i>

1:04:44.166 --> 1:04:47.458
<i>Round three. Who will it be?</i>

1:04:47.500 --> 1:04:50.333
<i>Oh...here goes nothing.</i>

1:04:50.375 --> 1:04:52.416
<i>Hey! You hear that, Sunny?</i>

1:04:52.458 --> 1:04:55.416
<i>Feel the rhythm take you over.</i>

1:04:55.458 --> 1:04:58.375
<i>- You're feeling it?</i>
<i>- I'm feeling it!</i>

1:04:58.416 --> 1:05:00.500
<i>- I'm feeling it!</i>
<i>- Yeah, you are, Sunny!</i>

1:05:00.541 --> 1:05:03.875
<i>- Yeah, you do this, honey!</i>
<i>- (MUSIC PLAYS)</i>

1:05:09.166 --> 1:05:11.208
<i>Yes! She's doing it, she's doing it!</i>

1:05:13.083 --> 1:05:14.750
<i>(CRITTER SQUEAKS)</i>

1:05:23.791 --> 1:05:25.125
<i>(DING-DING-DING!)</i>

1:05:27.875 --> 1:05:29.041
<i>We won.</i>

1:05:29.083 --> 1:05:32.208
<i>- We won! We actually won!</i>
<i>- Yes!</i>

1:05:32.250 --> 1:05:33.416
<i>(ALL CHEER)</i>

1:05:37.958 --> 1:05:39.541
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

1:05:39.583 --> 1:05:41.458
<i>An earth pony.</i>

1:05:41.500 --> 1:05:44.458
<i>- And pegasi.</i>
<i>- And a unicorn!</i>

1:05:44.500 --> 1:05:46.916
<i>Which you knew already.</i>

1:05:46.958 --> 1:05:50.166
<i>I know it doesn't look like it,</i>
<i>but we're here to help.</i>

1:05:50.208 --> 1:05:54.708
<i>Help? We don't need help,</i>
<i>especially from ponies like you.</i>

1:05:54.750 --> 1:05:56.166
<i>Give me the crystal.</i>

1:05:56.208 --> 1:05:57.583
<i>But I won!</i>

1:05:57.625 --> 1:05:59.291
<i>You tricked me.</i>

1:05:59.333 --> 1:06:00.833
<i>The crystal.</i>

1:06:02.875 --> 1:06:03.916
<i>Now!</i>

1:06:03.958 --> 1:06:06.708
<i>Uh...magic! Wing! Feather!</i>

1:06:06.750 --> 1:06:08.458
<i>Mayonnaise!</i>

1:06:08.500 --> 1:06:10.583
<i>- Bing!</i>
<i>- Bong.</i>

1:06:10.625 --> 1:06:12.083
<i>- Bing-bong!</i>
<i>- Bing-bong!</i>

1:06:12.125 --> 1:06:14.166
<i>- Bing-bong!</i>
<i>- Go, go, go!</i>

1:06:14.208 --> 1:06:17.458
<i>(BING-BONGING IN BACKGROUND)</i>

1:06:17.500 --> 1:06:18.875
<i>- You'll pay for this!</i>
<i>- Bing-bong!</i>

1:06:18.916 --> 1:06:20.375
<i>Sorry about that!</i>

1:06:20.416 --> 1:06:22.708
<i>- Uh...thanks for the tea!</i>
<i>- Bing-bong!</i>

1:06:26.666 --> 1:06:27.791
<i>(ALL GASP)</i>

1:06:29.291 --> 1:06:31.333
<i>Oh!</i>

1:06:31.375 --> 1:06:32.458
<i>Mom?</i>

1:06:32.500 --> 1:06:34.375
<i>Oh, my darlings.</i>

1:06:34.416 --> 1:06:36.166
<i>Thank hoofness you escaped.</i>

1:06:36.208 --> 1:06:37.666
<i>How did you find us?</i>

1:06:37.708 --> 1:06:38.958
<i>(BUSHES RUSTLE)</i>

1:06:39.000 --> 1:06:40.458
<i>Argh!</i>

1:06:41.458 --> 1:06:43.625
<i>Oh, my badge, yes!</i>

1:06:43.666 --> 1:06:46.875
<i>Oh, I'm so glad</i>
<i>I found my little fillies.</i>

1:06:46.916 --> 1:06:49.375
<i>Now, I know that if you just</i>
<i>come back with me,</i>

1:06:49.416 --> 1:06:51.458
<i>we can explain everything.</i>

1:06:51.500 --> 1:06:53.916
<i>Spin the story,</i>
<i>and they'll love us again.</i>

1:06:53.958 --> 1:06:55.541
<i>- Right?</i>
<i>- (HOOVES THUD)</i>

1:06:57.333 --> 1:06:59.708
<i>- Let us explain.</i>
<i>- There she is!</i>

1:06:59.750 --> 1:07:01.125
<i>Your Criminal Highness.</i>

1:07:01.166 --> 1:07:02.625
<i>You're coming with us.</i>

1:07:02.666 --> 1:07:04.541
<i>Argh! Unicorns!</i>

1:07:07.333 --> 1:07:09.916
<i>Give me back my crystals</i>
<i>and leave Bridlewood.</i>

1:07:09.958 --> 1:07:12.416
<i>Your crystals?</i>
<i>That crystal belongs to me.</i>

1:07:12.458 --> 1:07:16.000
<i>Not any more, it doesn't.</i>
<i>I won it fair and square.</i>

1:07:16.041 --> 1:07:17.750
<i>Huh! I certainly doubt it.</i>

1:07:17.791 --> 1:07:19.375
<i>Unicorns are known to be cheaters.</i>

1:07:19.416 --> 1:07:22.625
<i>You pegasi always thought</i>
<i>you were better than us.</i>

1:07:22.666 --> 1:07:24.416
<i>Hey, that's our queen</i>
<i>you're talking to.</i>

1:07:24.458 --> 1:07:25.500
<i>She's not a queen here.</i>

1:07:25.541 --> 1:07:27.833
<i>- Who do you think you are?</i>
<i>- We're gonna zap you with our horns!</i>

1:07:27.875 --> 1:07:29.458
<i>- This is our land!</i>
<i>- You're not welcome here!</i>

1:07:29.500 --> 1:07:32.250
<i>Surrender the crystal</i>
<i>or I'll use my powers against you.</i>

1:07:32.291 --> 1:07:34.000
<i>I'd like to see you try.</i>

1:07:34.041 --> 1:07:36.333
<i>No pony has magic!</i>

1:07:37.833 --> 1:07:39.000
<i>UNICORN: Bing-bong!</i>

1:07:39.041 --> 1:07:41.541
<i>But we are here to bring it back.</i>

1:07:41.583 --> 1:07:42.833
<i>Is it possible?</i>

1:07:42.875 --> 1:07:44.875
<i>- Did she just say magic?</i>
<i>- This is a trick.</i>

1:07:44.916 --> 1:07:47.708
<i>I know it sounds unbelievable,</i>

1:07:47.750 --> 1:07:50.750
<i>but please, just let us try.</i>

1:07:50.791 --> 1:07:53.166
<i>Please, Mom, trust us.</i>

1:07:53.208 --> 1:07:54.708
<i>You two...</i>

1:07:54.750 --> 1:07:56.000
<i>Fine.</i>

1:07:56.041 --> 1:07:57.666
<i>You're wasting your time, kid.</i>

1:07:59.791 --> 1:08:01.416
<i>Ready, Izzy?</i>

1:08:01.458 --> 1:08:02.958
<i>Ready.</i>

1:08:25.541 --> 1:08:26.833
<i>It... It...</i>

1:08:26.875 --> 1:08:29.125
<i>Why didn't it work, Daddy?</i>

1:08:29.166 --> 1:08:31.375
<i>Cos it was all just make-believe.</i>

1:08:31.416 --> 1:08:32.666
<i>We can try it again!</i>

1:08:32.708 --> 1:08:35.875
<i>Maybe...</i>
<i>Maybe we did it wrong somehow.</i>

1:08:37.000 --> 1:08:39.041
<i>Wait, wait, don't go.</i>

1:08:39.083 --> 1:08:40.291
<i>Oh, come on.</i>

1:08:40.333 --> 1:08:43.375
<i>Work! Work. Please work.</i>

1:08:43.416 --> 1:08:45.333
<i>- Come on.</i>
<i>- Sunny.</i>

1:08:45.375 --> 1:08:46.791
<i>It's OK.</i>

1:08:46.833 --> 1:08:48.166
<i>You did everything you could.</i>

1:08:48.208 --> 1:08:51.958
<i>I... I thought it would work.</i>

1:08:52.000 --> 1:08:54.541
<i>I was so, so sure of it.</i>

1:09:01.333 --> 1:09:03.833
<i>What do we do now, Sunny?</i>

1:09:10.708 --> 1:09:13.375
<i>I'm sorry for all the trouble</i>
<i>I caused you.</i>

1:09:15.750 --> 1:09:17.583
<i>PIPP: Sunny! We can't give up.</i>

1:09:18.791 --> 1:09:21.500
<i>I thought that I could make</i>
<i>a difference.</i>

1:09:26.375 --> 1:09:30.333
<i>But everywhere I go,</i>
<i>I just make things worse.</i>

1:09:30.375 --> 1:09:32.041
<i>That's not true.</i>

1:09:32.083 --> 1:09:34.458
<i>We're all in this together, right?</i>

1:09:34.500 --> 1:09:36.416
<i>- Yeah.</i>
<i>- Of course.</i>

1:09:36.458 --> 1:09:39.958
<i>I'm so sorry I let you all down.</i>

1:09:51.458 --> 1:09:53.375
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

1:09:53.416 --> 1:09:56.708
<i>I guess this is goodbye...friends.</i>

1:09:56.750 --> 1:09:59.333
<i>Better hurry...Sheriff.</i>

1:10:23.333 --> 1:10:25.666
<i>I'm right here if you need to talk,</i>
<i>Sunny.</i>

1:10:30.916 --> 1:10:31.916
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

1:10:44.791 --> 1:10:46.208
<i>(DOOR CLOSES)</i>

1:10:53.291 --> 1:10:54.791
<i>(SIGHS)</i>

1:12:41.166 --> 1:12:42.291
<i>(DOOR OPENS)</i>

1:12:42.333 --> 1:12:44.291
<i>- Sunny!</i>
<i>- Hitch! Hitch!</i>

1:12:44.333 --> 1:12:46.791
<i>I figured it out! There's actually...</i>

1:12:46.833 --> 1:12:48.000
<i>(BANG)</i>

1:12:58.250 --> 1:12:59.500
<i>Huh?</i>

1:12:59.541 --> 1:13:01.666
<i>What-What is going on here?</i>

1:13:01.708 --> 1:13:04.583
<i>We can't tell you. We've signed</i>
